Umubare wiyongereye cyane w'ubwandu bwa Coronavirus (COVID-19) mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abarwayi ba Coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ibintu bisa mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, byemeza ko nubwo ibihe bitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirimo kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ibyabaye mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bafite uburwayi bukomeye bigomba kurushaho kwitegura umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bitaro bya ICU.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari amakuru y'abantu benshi bari barwaye indwara y'ibihaha (pneumonia) i Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa coronavirus 2 ifitanye isano n'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara ya koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hafi 80% by'abantu banduye COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga ko barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero ariko ntibagaragaze ibimenyetso, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, uburwayi bwa COVID-19 bwazamuye cyane bigatuma umuntu akenera kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe abasigaye bagera kuri 6% bari bafite uburwayi bukomeye bukeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 wari hafi 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye uko imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 yifashe muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza (UK) tugereranya n'iyo mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'iy'abanduye mu Butaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'ibyabaye mu Bushinwa, COVID-19 ikomeje gukwirakwira hirya no hino ku isi kandi ikomeje kugenda ikwirakwira no mu bindi bihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nomero ya EuroSurveillance yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri n'abandi batangaje ko habayeho abantu ba mbere bo mu Burayi bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 nk'uko byasobanuwe n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS).
Mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe n'u Bufaransa batangajwe ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bavumbuwe mu bihugu byose 30 bya EU/AEA n'u Bwongereza (UK), aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza kuri uyu munsi, hari abantu 39,768 banduye n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, mu Butaliyani honyine hakaba hari abantu 17,750 banduye n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye.
Kugira umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 n'imiterere y'ubwandu
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara (ECDC), gitanga amakuru y'ibanze ku bihugu byose byo ku isi ku mibare y'abanduye COVID-19, iboneka gusa mu makuru y'ibiro by'ibanze nk'ibiro by'ubuzima by'ibihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'intara n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 iteye mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza no kuyigereranya n'iyo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'ikigereranyo cyo gukwirakwira kw'abanduye COVID-19, twabaze imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14, hanyuma tureba uko COVID-19 yagendaga, mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza, hagati ya tariki ya 1 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twatangaga kandi imibare y'ibanze y'abanduye muri buri gihugu kuva ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo, tugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza
Imiterere y'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza yakurikije iy'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 yatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma yiyongera cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Igitabo cy'inyongera).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'umubare w'abanduye bavuzwe mu Butaliyani, ariko ibihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byerekanye ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye (Igitabo cy'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Yashimangiye ko guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye bose, ubu ungana n'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu bishize cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongera cyane mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere igaragara mu mubare w'abanduye COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo kirimo kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
