Kugeza ubu, amakuru ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 muri EU/EEA araboneka ku bantu 6% na 1% (amakuru ntaragaragazwa).
