Iyi raporo igamije gusubiramo iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi mu gice gishya kandi kivugurura vuba.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na COV, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, icyorezo cy'umwaka wa 2012).
