Virusi za corona zisanzwe zisanzwe zigerageza gutera indwara zidakomeye mu bantu, kandi ahanini ziterwa na 15% by'ibicurane bya 4 bikunze kubaho.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana twahuye na Coronaviruses ebyiri zateye indwara zikomeye mu bantu, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye iki cyorezo gitangira mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu byinshi ku kigero cyo kwiyongera n'urupfu biteye ubwoba.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya coronavirus mu mateka y'abantu.
