Ibyinshi mu bikoresho bikora biracyari mu ibanga kuko bigoye kubikuramo no kugenzura ibyo bikoresho cyangwa uburyo bwiza bwo kubishyira hamwe.
Muri iki gihe, kubera ko nta muti wihariye kandi ufasha COVID-19, ubuvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa bwabaye bumwe mu buryo bw'ingenzi bwo kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa byoroheje cyangwa abakize indwara zikomeye.
Urugero, imiti ya Shu Feng Ji Do na Lian Hua King Wen yagaragaye ko igira ingaruka nziza mu kuvura COVID-19.
