Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Paul Chang na bagenzi be mu kazi basohoye inyigo igereranya uburyo bwo kuvura bw'imiti y'iburengerazuba (WM) bwonyine n'uburyo bwo kuvura buhuriweho bw'imiti y'iburengerazuba n'imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa.
Basanze igihe cyo gukira indwara y'umuriro mwinshi, kugabanya ibimenyetso no kuguma mu bitaro ari gito cyane mu baganga bavuraga mu bihugu by'iburengerazuba n'abavuraga mu Bushinwa, ugereranyije n'abavuraga mu bihugu by'iburengerazuba gusa.
Igishishikaje kurushaho, ni uko igipimo cy'indwara z'ibicurane (z'indwara z'ibicurane n'iz'ibicurane) cyari gito cyane mu itsinda ry'imiti y'Iburengerazuba + imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa ugereranyije n'itsinda ry'imiti y'Iburengerazuba yonyine (7.4% ugereranyije na 46.2%), kandi umubare w'abapfa wari muto mu itsinda ry'imiti y'Iburengerazuba + imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa ugereranyije n'itsinda ry'imiti y'Iburengerazuba yonyine (8.8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Nyamara, ubuvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa bugira ingaruka nziza kandi bufite umutekano, ariko buracyategereje kugeragezwa neza ku kigero kinini no mu bigo byinshi.
Byashimishije kandi gusobanura uburyo bwo gukora no gusobanura ingirakamaro z'imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa cyangwa uburyo ikoreshwa niba bishoboka.
Abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bafite COVID-19 akenshi bagira ubwoba bw'indwara yandura cyane ndetse no gupfa, kandi abantu bari mu kato barambiwe, bafite irungu n'uburakari.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'indwara nk'umuriro mwinshi, guhumana kw'umwuka, no gukorora, kimwe n'ingaruka mbi z'imiti, nk'ibitotsi biterwa n'imiti ituma umuntu agira imihangayiko myinshi n'indwara zo mu mutwe.
Mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'icyorezo cya SARS, hari amakuru avuga indwara zitandukanye z'imitekerereze zirimo kwiheba, guhangayika, ubwoba, guhungabana, ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe, ubwirasi ndetse no kwiyahura.
Gukurikirana no kwisanzura by'agateganyo, nk'igice cy'ibisubizo by'ubuzima rusange ku cyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu barushaho guhangayika no kwicira urubanza ku ngaruka z'ubwandu, kwisanzura no gushyira ikizinga ku miryango yabo n'incuti zabo.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu barwaye COVID-19, abakekwaho kuyandura, abahuye na bo n'abandi bantu bose babikeneye, bagomba guhabwa ubuvuzi bwo mu mutwe.
Ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho amatsinda y'indwara zo mu mutwe, ahantu hatandukanye ho kuvugana hagaragara hagenewe amakuru y'igihe cyose kandi y'ukuri ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n'imigambi yo kugivura, no gukoresha ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'imikorere byabugenewe kugira ngo hatagira uhatera.
Inkingo z'ingirakamaro zo guca uruziga rw'ubwandu bwa virusi kuva ku matungo n'abantu banduye kugeza ku bantu bashobora kuyandura ni ngombwa kandi akenshi zikoreshwa nk'inkunga yo kurwanya virusi mu kurwanya ibyorezo biterwa na virusi zigezweho.
Hakozwe imbaraga zo gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri poroteyine S zo gukora abasirikare b'umubiri batagira icyo bakora, bafite ubushobozi kandi barambye, no/cyangwa ubudahangarwa bwo kwirinda SARS-CoV.
Inkingo z'ubuzima z'ubwoko bwa SARS zagiye zigeragezwa mu ngero z'inyamaswa.
Icyakora, nta kintu na kimwe cyerekana ko izo nkingo z'abakandida z'inzobere z'abantu bakuze, z'abantu bafite ubumuga bwo kutabona n'iz'abantu bafite ubumuga bwo kutabona, n'iz'abantu barwaye virusi z'inyamaswa zituruka ku mutungo, zigeze zigerwaho mbere y'uko ikigo gitangira gukora ubushakashatsi.
Ibyo bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS imaze imyaka 17 itakiriho kandi nta muntu mushya wigeze uvugwa kuva icyo gihe.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, hari udukoko dutandukanye na MERS dukomeje kugaragara mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati kandi tukagera no mu tundi duce bitewe n'uko inyamaswa zikomeje kuboneka mu duce twanduye.
Uburyo bwo gukingira MERS bwakozwe hakoreshejwe virusi idakora, plasma ya ADN ya RBD idafite ogisijeni, utwo twuma tw'ubwandu, utuntu duto cyane, utuntu tumeze nk'ubwandu, n'uduporotine tw'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe, kandi bimwe muri byo byasuzumwe mu ngero z'inyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rwiza kandi rwiza rwa SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu badafite ubudahangarwa ni igikorwa cyihutirwa kandi gikomeye cyo kurwanya icyorezo kiriho.
Icyakora, gutsinda iki kibazo ni ikibazo gikomeye bitewe n'igihe kirekire (ku kigereranyo cy'amezi 18) gikenewe kugira ngo haboneke urukingo n'ihindagurika ry'indwara za koronavirusi.
COVID-19, nk'indwara nshya, itangiye kugaragaza uburyo bwayo bwose mu barwayi ibihumbi.
Mu bihe byinshi, abarwayi bashobora gukira buhoro buhoro nta ngaruka.
Icyakora, COVID-19, kimwe na SARS na MERS, ifitanye isano n'ubwandu bwinshi n'urupfu rw'abarwayi barembye cyane.
Kubaka uburyo bwo kwitegereza uko indwara ziza kugenda rero ni ngombwa ku bigo by'ubuzima kugira ngo bibanze bitange serivisi, cyane cyane mu duce dufite amikoro make.
Dushingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe kugeza ubu, ibintu bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka ku byitezwe ku barwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa bifitanye isano na byo (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe 33):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni yo yari ingenzi mu kwemeza uko SARS ishobora kwibasira abantu, kandi ni na ko bimeze kuri COVID-19.
Abantu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65 nibo banduye COVID-19, aho 47.7% by'abo barwayi barengeje imyaka 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866 nk'uko byagaragajwe haruguru.
Abarwayi bari bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi kandi bari bakuru cyane kurusha abatabufite (umushahara ungana n'imyaka 66 ugereranyije na 51), ibyo bikaba byerekana ko imyaka ari ikintu kigaragaza ingaruka z'abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abagabo benshi kurusha abagore (0.31/100,000 ugereranyije na 0.27/100,000), nk'uko byagaragajwe haruguru.
Indwara n'ibibazo biterwa n'indwara: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane barushaho kurwara indwara z'umutima zikomeye n'umutima udakora neza.
Indwara y'umutima kandi ni yo mpamvu nyamukuru y'urupfu mu barwayi ba SARS.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no guhuza ingirabuzimafatizo z'umushongi zishimishije na angiotensin-2 ikora mu mpyiko, bigatuma impyiko zidakora neza mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ni ngombwa kumenya ko imyaka n'uburwayi biri mu buryo bukomeye kandi bishobora guhura.
Ibisubizo bidasanzwe: Igipimo cya poroteyine igira ibyiyumvo C (CRP) mu maraso kigaragaza uburemere bw'ubuhumekero cyangwa imvune mu ngingo, kandi byemejwe ko ari ikintu cyerekana indwara, gusubiza imiti no gukira burundu.
Hari kandi isano yagaragajwe hagati y'urugero rwa poroteyine C igira ingaruka n'uburemere bw'indwara ya COVID-19 n'igihe izamara.
Uretse ibyo, kongera ingano ya LDH, AST, ALT na CK nabyo bishobora gufasha mu kwemeza ibizagerwaho.
Izi enzymes zigaragara cyane mu ngingo nyinshi, cyane cyane mu mutima n'umwijima, kandi zirasohoka mu gihe imyakura yangiritse.
Ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe by'uburwayi bw'umutima cyangwa impyiko.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'ubuvuzi: Igishushanyo cy'igituza n'iterambere ry'ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi hamwe n'ibindi bibazo bigomba kwitabwaho mu kwemeza ibisubizo bya COVID-19 n'ibyago byayo.
Gukoresha imiti igabanya ubukana: Nkuko byavuzwe haruguru, imiti igabanya ubukana ikoreshwa cyane nk'umuti wunganira indwara zitandura mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ibyangiritse.
Kuva habaho gukoresha cyane ibipimo byinshi bya 'hormones stimulants' ku barwayi ba SARS, abenshi mu barokotse uburwayi bwa 'osteonecrosis' bafite ubumuga bw'ubuzima bwose n'ubuzima bubi.
Ku bw'ibyo, imiti igabanya ubukana ikwiye gukoreshwa mu buryo buciriritse kandi bw'igihe gito mu barwayi ba COVID-19, niba ari ngombwa.
Umunaniro wo mu mutwe: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19, abarwayi benshi bagize umunaniro udasanzwe; akenshi bahoraga mu kato igihe kirekire, bahorana amakenga menshi, kandi bibonera urupfu rw'abagize umuryango wabo na bagenzi babo barwaye.
Ni ngombwa gutanga ubujyanama mu by'imitekerereze no gushyigikira abarwayi igihe kirekire kugira ngo babafashe gukira stress no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu kugeza ubu, COVID-19 isa n'ifite ibimenyetso by'icyorezo bitandukanye n'icya SARS.
Uretse kuba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kuvukira mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, ishobora no kuvukira mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru kandi igatuma ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso na mba mu gihe cy'ubwandu, kimwe n'izindi koronavirusi zitera ibicurane.
Ku bw'ibyo, abarwayi banduye mu gihe cya mbere cyangwa mu gihe cy'uburwayi bashobora gukora virusi nyinshi mu bikorwa byabo bya buri munsi, bigatuma kurwanya icyorezo bigorana.
Icyakora, byatangiye gufatwa ko SARS-CoV yandura iyo abarwayi barwaye cyane, mu gihe ubwandu bwinshi bwa virusi butigeze bubaho mu gihe cya mbere.
Ku bw'ibyo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu kirakomeye cyane kandi kiragoye kugenzura kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Muri iki gihe, mu Bushinwa hari imihati ikomeye irimo ikorwa, harimo gufunga Wuhan n'imijyi ihakikije no gushyira abaturage bose mu kato, mu rwego rwo guhashya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo izo ngamba zangije ubukungu n'ibindi bice by'igihugu, umubare w'abarwayi bashya uragenda ugabanuka, bikaba bigaragaza ko icyorezo kigabanuka.
Igitekerezo cyiza ni uko iki cyorezo kizarangira muri Werurwe, maze iki cyorezo kigahera mu mezi atatu cyangwa ane.
Nyamara, hari abandi bahanga batagira icyizere nk'icyo.
Paul Hunter n'abandi, bavuze ko COVID-19, isa n'iyandura cyane kurusha SARS, itazarangira mu 2020.
Ira Longini n'abandi bakoze uburyo bwo guhanura ingaruka z'icyorezo, batanga igitekerezo cy'uko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwanduza bibiri bya gatatu by'abatuye isi.
Itsinda ry'Abanyakanada ryatangaje ko SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu bipimo byo mu muhogo no mu muhogo by'abarwayi bakize kandi basohotse ibitaro mu byumweru bibiri bishize, byerekana ko virusi nshya ishobora guhora ibaho nk'ibicurane.
Nyamara, hari ibimenyetso by'uko mu Bushinwa hari icyizere bitewe n'umubare w'abanduye mushya ugabanuka, byerekana ko ingamba zariho zishobora kuba zaragize icyo zigeraho.
Ebola yari yitezwe mbere ko ishobora guhitana abantu bagera kuri miliyoni imwe.
Icyakora, iyi ndwara yaje kugenzurwa hakurikijwe ingamba zikomeye zo kwitandukanya n'abandi.
Birashoboka ko kimwe na SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba idashobora kwanduza cyane, amaherezo igashira cyangwa ikaba virusi idashobora kwanduza cyane kandi ikanabana n'abantu.
Dore aho COVID-19 yagereranyijwe na SARS na MERS (ishusho 55).
SARS-CoV-2 yandura cyane iyo ukoroye cyangwa ukoroye, kandi ishobora kwandura binyuze mu guhura n'ibintu byanduye virusi.
Virusi kandi yagaragaye mu musarani, bituma habaho uburyo bushya bwo kwandura binyuze mu musarani ujya mu kanwa.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku bantu 138 bwagaragaje ko 41% by'abo bantu bashobora kuba baranduye indwara zo mu bitaro, harimo 17 barwaye izindi ndwara no kuba ari abaganga 40.
Ni yo mpamvu, hagomba gufatwa ingamba zikomeye zo kurinda abantu, cyane cyane abashinzwe ubuzima, abakozi b'imibereho myiza, abagize umuryango, abo bakorana ndetse n'abagenzi bagiranye isano n'abarwayi cyangwa abantu banduye.
Kwambara udupfukamunwa ni wo murongo wa mbere wo kwirinda ushobora gukoreshwa mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura; gukoresha udupfukamunwa two mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi n'udupfukamunwa two guhumeka twitwa N95 (Uruzitiro rwa 1860s) bifasha mu kugenzura ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi turinda amazi atemba ava ku muntu ushobora kuba yanduye gukwirakwira mu mwuka cyangwa kwifatanya n'ibintu, bityo akaba ashobora gukwirakwira ku bandi.
Nyamara, udupfukamunwa twa N95 (urukurikirane rwa 1860s) dushobora kurinda gusa guhumeka ferryones nto cyane iri hagati ya 10 na 80 nm, hamwe na 5% gusa ya ferryones ishoboye kwinjira byuzuye; SARS-CoV-2 isa na SARS-CoV mu bunini kandi buri imwe ifite ingano ya 85 nm.
Kubera ko utwo duce dushobora kwinjira mu masike eshanu z'ubuvuzi ziteretse hamwe, abavura bahuye n'abarwayi bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa twa N95 (Urunani rwa 1860s) ariko si udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi.
Uretse udupfukamunwa, abavura bagomba kwambara imyenda ikwiriye yo kwicungira kugira ngo badakomeza guhura na virusi.
Virusi kandi zishobora kwanduza umuntu binyuze mu maso.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; birashoboka ko virusi yinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu maso ye arwaye.
Ku bw'ibyo, abavura bagomba no kwambara udukingirizo cyangwa amadarubindi mu gihe bakorana n'abarwayi.
Ku bantu muri rusange bari mu duce twatewe cyangwa dushobora kuba twatewe, barasabwa cyane gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune n'isuku nyinshi, kugerageza kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bagire isuku no kugabanya guhura n'abantu bashobora kuba baranduye.
Intera y'ibirenge bitatu ni nziza ku bantu batandukanye n'umurwayi.
Ibyo ni uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ndetse no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 yaje mu isi nk'agakoko gashya, kuba isa cyane na SARS-CoV nk'uko byatangajwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 byari gutuma mu Bushinwa haba ubukangurambaga bukabije hashingiwe ku kwibuka cyane ko habayeho icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003.
Icyakora, ku itariki ya 19 Mutarama 2020, umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe kurwanya indwara yijeje abaturage ko iyi virusi nshya ifite ubwandu buciriritse, ko ikwirakwira buciriritse hagati y'abantu kandi ko nta kibazo cyo kwirinda no kuyihashya.
Ubwo butumwa bwagabanyije cyane ubushishozi bw'abaturage muri rusange, cyane cyane ubwo igihugu cyose cyari kigiye kwitegura ibirori byo kwizihiza Umunsi Mukuru w'Ubutwari, igihe gikomeye cyo kugabanya ubwandu bw'iki cyorezo mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ibigo by'ubuvuzi byo mu Bushinwa bishobora kungukirwa n'iyo nyigisho mbi kandi bigakora ibishoboka byose mu gihe kizaza.
Urugero, ibi bigo bigomba (1) kwitonda cyane mu gutanga amakuru y'abaturage kuko ijambo ryose rifite agaciro ku baturage kandi rishobora guhindura imyitwarire n'ibyemezo byabo; (2) kurushaho kumva no kugira icyo bakora ku makuru adasanzwe aturuka mu mavuriro aho gutegereza raporo z'ibanze z'abaganga cyangwa abayobozi; (3) kurushaho guhagarika icyorezo gishobora kwaduka mu gihe cya mbere aho kugerageza guhumuriza abaturage; (4) kurushaho gutanga imyitozo igamije kandi ikora neza yo kongera ubwitonzi bw'abaturage ku ndwara z'ibyorezo no kugerageza no kunoza gahunda y'ubutabazi bw'abaturage.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 cyatangiye mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, yakwirakwiriye mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo ku isi.
Kubera ko virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso bikaba bisa cyane na COVID-19 na SARS, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye abantu benshi barwara SARS.
Icyakora, hari itandukaniro rikomeye hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, ari ngombwa mu guhashya icyorezo no kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato, abagabo kurusha abagore, kandi ubukana n'urupfu na byo biri hejuru mu bantu bakuze kurusha mu bakiri bato.
SARS ifite igipimo cy'urupfu kiri hejuru ya COVID-19 (10.91% ugereranyije na 1.44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakwirakwiza virusi nubwo nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS bo bakunze kuyikwirakwiza iyo barwaye cyane, bigatuma kurwanya ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 bitoroha.
Ibi bisobanuye mu rugero runaka impamvu SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira vuba kandi cyane kurusha SARS-CoV.
Igishushanyo cya SARS-CoV-2 cy'insoro cy'abantu bamwe na bamwe barwaye COVID-19 gishobora kuba kibi.
Ku rundi ruhande, abarwayi bakize bashobora kongera kwandura iyo virusi.
Ibi byongera cyane ibyago byo gukwirakwira kwa virusi.
Nubwo ubushakashatsi kuri COVID-19 bugenda bufata indi ntera, haracyari ibibazo byinshi bikomeye bigomba gukemurwa, nk'ibi bikurikira:
SARS-CoV-2 yavuye he?
Nubwo twabonye ko SARS-CoV-2 ihuriyeho na Coronaviruses mu bwoko bwa SARS mu birura, ntitwabasha kuvuga ko SARS-CoV-2 yaturutse mu birura.
Ni iyihe nyamaswa yari ubwoko bw'ibanze bwandurira virusi ku nyamaswa y'inkomoko, nk'imbeba, ikajya ku bantu?
Turamutse tutazi ibisubizo by'ibibazo bya mbere n'ibya kabiri, ntidushobora guhagarika ubwandu mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza, kandi bwongera kugaruka igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Nubwo uburyo bwa molekile n'ibizamini bya biochimique byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano na angiotensin 2 ikora mu buryo bw'indwara, ni gute virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuyoboro w'umwuka igatera impinduka zishimishije nyuma?
Ese iyi virusi ifitanye isano n'utundi duce tw'umubiri dutanga angiotensin 2?
Tudafite ibisubizo byumvikana kuri ibyo bibazo, ntidushobora gukora ibizamini byihuse kandi byuzuye no gutanga imiti ikora.
Iki cyorezo kizakomeza kugeza ryari?
Ni gute virusi ihinduka mu buryo bw'imiterere mu gihe ikwirakwira hagati y'abantu?
Ese izatera icyorezo ku isi, cyangwa izashira nk'icyorezo cya SARS, cyangwa izagaruka mu buryo buhoraho nk'ibicurane?
Ni ngombwa ariko bishobora gufata igihe kugira ngo ushakishe ibisubizo by'ibibazo biri hejuru n'ibindi byinshi.
Nyamara, uko byagenda kose, nta kundi twabigenza uretse guhagarika iki cyorezo vuba na bwangu no gusubiza ubuzima bwacu mu buryo busanzwe.
Inkomoko y'inyamaswa ya koronavirusi y'umuntu
Guhinduka no guhuza n'imiterere byateye iterambere ry'ubwoko bwa koronavirusi n'abanduye, harimo n'abantu, mu myaka ibihumbi n'ibihumbi ishize.
Mbere ya 2003, hari ubwoko bubiri bwa koronavirusi bw'umuntu (CoVs) bwari buzwiho gutera indwara zidakomeye, nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya SARS na MERS byerekana indi nzira, bigaragaza ko ubwandu bwa koronavirusi bukomeye kandi bushobora guhitana ubuzima.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu Bushinwa rwagati mu mpera za 2019 yatumye koronavirusi yongera kugaragara, kandi twatangajwe n'uko yakwirakwiriye vuba ariko ifite ubushobozi bwo gutera indwara ugereranyije na mwene se SARS-CoV.
Coronavirus ni indwara ikomoka ku nyamaswa, bityo rero gusobanukirwa inkomoko y'inyamaswa za coronavirus byadufasha cyane.
Imirwi myinshi ya koronavirusi y'umuntu ituruka mu birura kuko nta ndwara ziterwa na byo.
Hari kandi abarwayi ba virusi ya corona zimwe na zimwe bazwiho kuba ari bo ba nyirazo.
Kugena inyamaswa z'abashyitsi bigira ingaruka ku burinzi bw'indwara z'abantu.
Gusuzuma isano iri hagati ya koronavirusi n'umwakira mu nyamaswa na byo bitanga isomo ry'ingenzi ku itangira ry'indwara ya koronavirusi mu bantu.
Muri iyi nkuru, turatanga isesengura ry'amakuru aboneka ku mikorobe zirindwi za koronavirusi, twibanda ku mateka y'ubumenyingiro bwazo, aho zakomotse n'imiterere yazo.
Icy'ingenzi kurushaho, turagereranya kandi turagaragaza coronavirus zitandukanye z'abantu duhereye ku buryo virusi ihindagurika n'uko genome ihinduka.
Muri iyi nkuru tugiye kuganira ku ndwara iterwa n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) kiriho ubu.
Byongeye kandi, byerekana kandi ibyo bisaba kugira ngo umukerarugendo ahinduke neza n'ingaruka z'ibibazo by'ihindagurika rya virusi ku buremere bw'indwara.
Virusi za corona (Coronaviruses) ni zo zigize umuryango wa coronaviruses, zigizwe n'itsinda ry'indwara zifite uruziga rumwe rw'umugozi wa RNA.
Izo virusi zifite genome nini cyane mu virusi zifite ADN ya riboze, iri hagati ya kilobasi 26 na 32 kandi zitwa "viruses coronaires" kubera ko zimeze nk'ikamba mu cyuma cya microscope.
Ku bijyanye n'imiterere, koronavirusi zifite genomes zidakoranywe ubuhanga zihuriyeho.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya genome bifite ibipimo bibiri by'ibanze by'ibanze by'ibanze (ORF1a na ORF1b), bihinduka ubwoko bw'ibimera byinshi bya pp1a na pp1ab.
Poroteyine nyinshi zongera gutunganywa kugira ngo zitange poroteyine 16 zitari iz'ubwubatsi, zigaragazwa nk'nsp1~16.
Igice gisigaye cya genome kirimo imiterere y'ibinyabuzima by'ingenzi, harimo S-spike, E-shell, M-membrane na N-DNA.
Imiryango itandukanye ya koronavirusi kandi ikoresha poroteyine nyinshi z'inyongera z'imiryango yihariye.
Bitewe n'itandukaniro mu mikoranire ya poroteyine, koronavirusi zigizwe n'ubwoko bune (koronavirusi ya alfa, koronavirusi ya beta, koronavirusi ya gamma, koronavirusi ya delta), muri bwo hakaba harimo ubwoko bwa koronavirusi ya beta, ikubiyemo koronavirusi nyinshi z'abantu, ikaba ifite imitwe ine (A, W, C, na D).
Ibihamya by'ihindagurika ry'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo byagaragaje ko udusimba n'imbeba ari byo byakomokaho virusi ya coronavirusi ya alpha na beta, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zikorera virusi ya coronavirusi ya gamma na delta.
Mu myaka ibihumbi, koronavirusi zakomeje kurenga inzitizi z'ubwoko, zimwe muri zo zigaragara nk'izitera indwara zikomeye mu bantu.
Kugeza ubu hamaze kumenyekana ubwoko bw'indwara ya Coronavirusi zigera kuri 7.
Muri izo virusi harimo koronavirusi ya HRV-229E na koronavirusi ya HRV-NL63, ari zo koronavirusi za alfa.
Izindi koronavirusi eshanu za beta zirimo koronavirusi ya OC43, koronavirusi ya HKU1, koronavirusi itera indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (SARS-CoV), koronavirusi itera indwara z'ubuhumekero zo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
Ubusanzwe, virusi ya coronavirusi ya 229E, virusi ya coronavirusi ya OC43, virusi ya coronavirusi ya HKU1 na virusi ya coronavirusi ya NL63 ituma habaho ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'ibicurane, igifu cyangwa byombi.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na virusi nshya izwi nka SARS-CoV-2 zose zateye indwara cyane, zitera indwara zikomeye zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero y'ibumoso ku barwayi benshi cyane bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ishozi (acute respiratory distress syndrome) n'indwara z'ubuhumekero butari uburwayi.
Coronavirus y'umuntu 229E, ubwoko bwa mbere B814, yabonetse mu muhogo w'abarwayi barwaye ibicurane mu myaka ya za 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, amakuru menshi yagiye akusanywa binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse ku virusi ya Corona-229E na OC-43, byibasira byonyine.
Mu by'ukuri, byari bisanzwe bizwi ko kwandura coronavirus nta cyo bitwaye kugeza igihe SARS izabonekera.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo byishe abantu benshi mu mateka yacu, aho abantu 8,000 banduye, naho abagera ku 10% bahitanwa na cyo.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) yongeye kwibasira cyane mu Karere ka Arabiya, ikwirakwira hirya no hino ku isi.
Virusi ya Coronavirusi nshya y'umuntu (CoV-2019), yiswe SARS-CoV-2, ni yo mpamvu y'icyorezo cy'indwara ya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), yahitanye abantu barenga 3,120 kandi yandura abantu barenga 91,000 ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Umuburo uratangiye kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Coronaviruses zose uko ari ndwi z'umuntu zifite inkomoko mu nyamaswa, ni ukuvuga mu birura, mu mbeba cyangwa mu nyamaswa zo mu rugo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko virusi zose za coronavirusi zaturutse ku bambu, kuko izo virusi ziba zisanzwe kandi zitatera indwara ariko zigaragaza amoko atandukanye y'ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, siyansi, imibereho myiza n'imyifatire mu Bushinwa no ku isi.
Gukurikirana inkomoko y'inyamaswa za koronavirusi z'umuntu byatanze urufatiro rwo gusobanukirwa amateka kamere, imbaraga zituma habaho no kugabanya uburyo bwo kwimuka hagati y'ubwoko.
Ibi bishobora no kuyobora cyangwa koroshya gushakisha ikigega, umukerarugendo n'inyamaswa zikura za SARS-CoV-2, hamwe n'ingaruka zikomeye zo kwirinda ingaruka z'igihe kizaza.
Muri iyi nkuru, turareba uko ubwoko bw'inyamaswa bwatangiye, uko bwagiye buhinduka, n'uko virusi ya corona zitera indwara.
By'umwihariko, turasuzuma kandi tugasobanura imyumvire ikwirakwizwa y'uko virusi z'inkomoko za koronavirusi zisanzwe zitatera indwara mu byibare byazo bisanzwe ariko zikaba zitera indwara iyo zinyuze mu bwoko bwazo zijya ku wundi muntu.
Turimo kandi gusuzuma uko coronavirus y'umuntu igenda kuko akenshi iyo ikwirakwira cyane usanga n'ubukana bwayo bugabanuka.
Muri iyo ngingo kandi, turaganira ku ngaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Coronaviruses zo mu matungo zamenyekanye kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1930.
Mbere y'uko ubwoko B814 bwa coronavirus ya 229E bw'umuntu bwigenga bwa mbere mu maraso y'abarwayi ba kasuzuguro, ubwoko butandukanye bwa coronavirus bwavumbuwe mu nyamaswa zitandukanye zanduye, harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, habonetse ubwoko burindwi bwa koronavirusi.
Gutanga igisubizo kigufi ku mateka y'ubumenyingiro bwa Coronavirus (Imbonerahamwe ya 1) bizaba ari inyigisho n'ubuyobozi.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa koronavirusi ya 229E bw'umuntu bwavumbuwe mu nzira y'ubuhumekero y'abarwayi barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo hejuru mu 1966, nyuma buza kwihanganira kubaho mu byiciro by'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye coronavirus ya 229E bagaragaza ibimenyetso bisanzwe by'ibicurane, birimo umutwe, gusuhererwa, kugira iseseme, kuribwa mu muhogo, hamwe n'umuriro, no kugira inyota mu bice 10 kugeza kuri 20%.
Nyuma mu 1967, virusi ya coronavirusi y'umuntu-OC43 yavuye mu kigo cy'imyororokere, nyuma ijya mu bwonko bw'abana b'imbeba.
Ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa coronavirus ya OC43 bisa n'ibya coronavirus ya 229E, idashobora gutandukanywa n'ibindi bikoko byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nka virusi ya grippe A na virus z'imuhengeri.
Virusi ya Coronavirusi ya 229E na OC43 zikwirakwira ku isi hose, kandi zikunze kwanduzwa mu gihe cy'itumba mu turere turimo ikirere cyiza.
Muri rusange, igihe izo virusi zombi zimara mu mubiri kitarenze icyumweru kimwe, bikurikirwa n'uburwayi mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bushake ku bantu, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye virusi ya coronavirusi ya 229E batangiye kurwara ibicurane byoroheje.
Abarwayi bake cyane bafite ubumuga bwo kutabona bagaragaje ubumuga bukomeye mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi.
SARS, izwi kandi nka "pneumonia non-infectieuse", ni icyorezo cya mbere cyatewe na coronavirus y'umuntu cyanditswe neza mu mateka y'abantu, kandi cyatewe na SARS-CoV, coronavirus ya gatatu y'umuntu ivumbuwe.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye SARS yavumbuwe mu mpera za 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyatumye abantu 8,096 banduye ndetse hapfa abantu 774, kandi cyakwirakwiriye mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Uretse uwanduza cyane, bivugwa ko ubwandu bumwe bushobora gutera ubwandu bubiri bw'ibanze, mu gihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro rw'iminsi ine kugeza kuri irindwi, kandi virusi igaragara cyane ku munsi wa 10.
