Virusi ya mbere yabonetse mu cyuma cyafashwe mu bihaha bya mwene wabo w'uwa mbere wanduye, wari wavuye i Guangzhou ajya i Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, hakozwe ubushakashatsi bwinshi kuri koronavirusi y'umuntu.
Virusi ya Coronavirusi y'umuntu-NL63 yabonetse mu mwana w'amezi 7 wo mu Buholandi mu mpera za 2004.
