Imbeho, indwara y'igifu, umuriro n'indwara y'ibisebe ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe by'indwara iterwa na HRV-NL63.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwigenga bwagaragaje ko virusi imwe yavuye mu cyuma cy'umuhogo w'umwana w'amezi 8 urwaye indwara y'ibihaha mu Buholandi.
Nubwo yavumbuwe mu Buholandi, ikwirakwira ku isi hose.
Bivugwa ko virusi ya coronavirusi ya NL63 itera hafi 4.7% by'indwara zisanzwe z'ubuhumekero, kandi ikagira ubukana bwinshi mu mpeshyi, mu itumba no mu itumba.
