Muri rusange, iyo izo koronavirusi zigejeje ubushobozi bwo kwimuka neza no gukomeza kwibeshaho mu bantu, ntizikunda kurwara cyane.
Mu 2012 nibwo bwa mbere MERS-CoV yabonetse mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wari urwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero n'impyiko muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Mu gihe abenshi mu banduye bagaragaye mu byiciro by'abanduye baturuka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi no muri Tuniziya, hari abanduye bavuye hanze, kandi hari n'abanduye mu buryo bw'ibanze.
