Kwiga coronavirus mu birura n'ibindi nyamaswa byahinduye cyane uko tubona akamaro k'inkomoko y'indwara z'amatungo n'ibikoresho by'inyamaswa bya coronavirus z'abantu mu kwanduzanya n'abantu.
Ibihamya bikomeye byerekana ko SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byose byakomotse ku mugozi w'inzoka kandi byandujwe ku bantu binyuze mu ba nyir'ubwite.
Kubera ko SARS-CoV yandura biturutse ku bantu bahura n'ingurube mu masoko, gufunga amasoko y'ibiribwa bihiye no kwica ingurube byagombaga gutuma icyorezo cya SARS kirangira.
Muri ubwo buryo, inyamaswa zirya ibiheri zigomba gucibwa ku masoko y'ibikoresho bishya kugira ngo birinde kwanduzanya indwara z'inyamaswa, bitewe n'uko mu birya ibiheri habonetse ubwoko bwinshi bwa virusi ya Corona beta, isa cyane na SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko, niba SARS-CoV-2 yanduye abantu cyangwa itayanduye, ndetse n'uburyo bwose yandura, binyuze mu nyamaswa zirya ibiheri n'ibindi nyamaswa z'inkazi, biracyari ikibazo gikeneye gusobanurwa mu bushakashatsi buzakorwa mu gihe kizaza.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubwiza bw'ibiti by'imyelayo bwonyine ni bwo bwabonetse mu gihe kirekire cyane.
Ubu bwiza ni uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo gutwara abantu, kandi ni isoko y'ingenzi y'inyama, amata, uruhu n'ibikomoka ku bwoya by'abaturage baho.
Ni ubwoko bw'ibinyamushongo bikunze kuboneka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati no muri Afurika.
Ku bw'ibyo, ntibishoboka gutakaza ibyiza byose kugira ngo MERS ihagarikwe, nk'uko abayobozi b'amasoko y'inyamaswa zo mu mashyamba mu Bushinwa babikoze mu kwirinda ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
Kugira ngo hahagarikwe ibyorezo bya MERS bikomeje, hakwiye gushyirwaho uburyo busesuye bwo gukora inkingo z'indwara ya MERS-CoV z'ubwiza, hamwe n'ibindi bikorwa byo kurwanya ubwandu.
Iyo tudashoboye kurandura burundu izo virusi, hari ubundi bwoko bushya bw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bushobora kuvuka, bukazana ibyorezo.
Hari ubwoko butandukanye bwa koronavirusi bufitanye isano n'indwara z'inyamaswa zituruka mu ishyamba.
By'umwihariko, koronavirusi zo mu birura ni nyinshi cyane, kandi zishobora gutera indwara z'inyamaswa.
Hari amahirwe menshi yo kuvuka no kongera kuvuka kwa koronavirusi zifitanye isano n'indwara z'inyamaswa, bigatuma habaho koronavirusi nshya zishobora kwanduza no kwica abantu mu gihe kizaza.
Mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'u Bushinwa, umuco wo kurya inyamaswa z'ishyamba wagombye kurekurwa kugira ngo abantu n'inyamaswa badakomeza guhura.
Mu gihe abantu bahanganye n'ibibazo by'indwara ya SARS, MERS na COVID-19, hagomba gushyirwaho gahunda ikwiriye yo kwitegura no guhangana na byo.
Ukuri ni uko virusi nyinshi zimaze igihe kirekire cyane ku isi.
Zibera mu bigega byazo bwite kugeza igihe zizabona uburyo bwo gukwirakwira no kororoka.
Nubwo udusimba dufite ibintu byinshi bituma virusi zishobora gukwirakwira, amahirwe y'uko abantu bazaba bahuye n'udusimba n'izindi nyamaswa zo mu gasozi ashobora kugabanuka mu gihe abantu bazaba bafite umuco wo kuzirinda.
Gukurikirana inyamaswa z'ibinyabuzima mu buryo buhoraho ni igikorwa cy'ingenzi mu gusobanukirwa neza ibidukikije bya koronavirusi n'ibikoresho byayo, bikaba bigaragaza akamaro kabyo mu kwirinda ko zikwirakwira ziva ku nyamaswa zijya ku bantu no kwirinda ko zishobora kuzongera kugaragara.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bw'inyamaswa ni ukubuza abantu kuba ahantu hazwi ho kubika virusi ziterwa n'inyamaswa.
Igitekerezo cy'inkomoko y'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 gikomeje kuba ikibazo gikomeye.
Icya mbere, niba udusimba twanduza SARS-CoV-2 udukoko turya ibinyamushongo, ni ngombwa kumenya imiterere y'aho udusimba n'utundi dukoko turya ibinyamushongo twajya mu bidukikije nk'ibyo.
Icya kabiri, niba udusimba tugira uruhare rugaragara mu kwanduza abantu, ubwo uburyo abantu babwirwaramo bugomba kugenzurwa.
Icya gatatu, niba ubwoko bwa gatatu bw'inyamaswa z'ibinyamaswa ari bwo bufite uruhare rw'inyamaswa nyirabwo, ubwo rero twagombye gusobanura uburyo buhuza n'ubwoko butandukanye, harimo abantu, udusimba n'ibinyamanswa by'ibinyamanswa.
Hanyuma, kubera ko inyamaswa nyinshi zirya ibinyamubiri harimo n'amatungo yo mu rugo zishobora gukekwaho kuba zitwaye SARS-CoV-2, hakwiye gukorwa igenzura n'igerageza ry'ubwandu.
Yaba nyir'ubwite ari ikimonyo, ikimonyo cy'inkende cyangwa ibindi nyamaswa, SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa virusi ya se ikomoka kuri yo ishobora kumenyekana nk'aho ari yo nyir'ubwite mu gihe kizaza.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeje muri uru rwego buzatuma tumenya uko SARS-CoV-2 yahindutse mu matungo, hamwe n'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda no kurwanya COVID-19 mu bantu.
Hakenewe kuvugurura ibipimo by'uburwayi bw'umwihariko "uburwayi bukekwa" n'"uburwayi bwemejwe" mu gihe umuntu avurwa ko arwaye COVID-19.
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryasohoye amabwiriza yihuse ku byerekeye gusuzuma no kuvura ubwandu bwa Coronavirus (CoV-2019) kandi ayo mabwiriza yatanze ubunararibonye bwacu kandi atanga amakuru y'ibanze akenewe mu kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi.
Nubwo icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ari icyorezo gishya, ubumenyi n'ubumenyi bwacu bugenda bwiyongera bufatiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ibigeragezo byo mu buvuzi; bityo rero, uburyo bwo gusuzuma no kuvura bugenda buvugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije ku bitekerezo byatanzwe na Ward ku mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya byo gusuzuma, "ikosa rikekwaho" na "ikosa ryemejwe", dukurikije amabwiriza mashya yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (Inyandiko ya karindwi) yatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abasangwabutaka y'u Bushinwa.
Mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019, icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (Coronavirus 2019), ubu kizwi ku mugaragaro nka Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) cyatangiye, maze kizwi nka Coronavirus 2 ifitanye isano n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryakoze amabwiriza yihuse kandi asohoka kuri interineti mu kinyamakuru cya Military Medical Research ku ya 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Yateje impungenge nyinshi kuva yashyirwa ahagaragara.
Nyamuneka menya ko nubwo COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite bigenda byiyongera bitewe n'ibisubizo by'ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ibigeragezo byo mu buvuzi; bityo rero, uburyo bwo gusuzuma no kuvura bugenda buvugururwa.
Urugero, amabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 yatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima muri Repubulika y'Abaturage y'u Bushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020, yasohotse mu mpinduka zirindwi zose hamwe n'impinduka zimwe na zimwe z'ingenzi.
