Bangladesh yongeye kugira abantu batanu bishwe na COVID-19, umubare munini w'abamaze gupfa ku munsi
Ejo Bangladesh yemeje ko abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye ku munsi umwe bazize iyi virus.
Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'ibyorezo (IEDCR) cyatangaje ko kugeza ejo, abamaze kwandura ari 114 mu gihe abamaze gukira ari 33 bari mu ngo.
Abantu 17 bapfuye.
Umuyobozi w'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu kurwanya indwara n'ibyorezo, Dr. Mirjadi Sabrina Flora, mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyabereye kuri interineti, yavuze ko abapfuye ari abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Nk'uko Dr. Mirjadi yabitangaje, hari abantu babiri bari bafite hejuru y'imyaka 60, babiri bari hagati y'imyaka 51 na 60, n'undi umwe wari hagati y'imyaka 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko babiri mu bapfuye ari abo mu mujyi wa Dhaka.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku Buzima (OMS) watangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe.
Umuyobozi w'ibitaro yabwiye ikigo cy'itangazamakuru cyo muri ako gace cya Anadolu ko umwe mu bapfuye ari Jalal Saif Rahman, umuyobozi wa Anti-Corruption Authority of Bangladesh, wari urwariye mu bitaro bya Kuwait Maitre.
Minisitiri w'ubwikorezi bw'ubutaka n'ibiraro muri Bangladesh, Ubeed al-Qadir, yavuze mu itangazo ryashyizwe kuri videwo kuri uyu wa Gatandatu ko imodoka z'abantu bose zizamara igihe kirekire kurusha uko byari biteganyijwe mbere, kugeza ku wa Gatandatu utaha.
Imodoka zitwara abagenzi zatangiye guhagarara ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, kandi byari biteganyijwe ko zihagarara ku wa Gatandatu tariki ya 4 Mata.
Ingendo z'ibintu by'ibanze biracyemewe: imiti, lisansi n'ibiribwa.
Abantu babiri bavuye mu Butaliyani n'umugore w'umwe muri bo ni bo banduye bwa mbere COVID-19 muri Bangladesh ku ya 8 Werurwe.
Bose uko ari batatu bari bamaze gukira ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe.
Umubare w'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 warenze miliyoni ku isi hose.
Ku wa Kane, amakuru yatanzwe na Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins yagaragaje ko umubare w'abantu banduye coronavirus itera indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS-CoV-2) urenga miliyoni ku isi.
COVID-19 iterwa na koronavirusi yahitanye abantu bagera ku bihumbi 52.
Iyi nkuru y'ubuhanuzi y'ibyago byabayeho ku munsi Malawi yemejeho ubwandu bwa mbere bwa coronavirus, ndetse n'urupfu rwa mbere rwayo muri Zambia.
Koreya ya Ruguru yatangaje ko kuva ku wa Kane, ari kimwe mu bihugu bike bikiri nta bantu banduye coronavirus.
