Amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya agabanya umubare w'impapuro z'isuku ku gicuruzwa
Ku mugoroba wo kuwa gatandatu no ku cyumweru, amaduka yo muri Australia yitwa Wallworths na Kohl's yatsimbaraye ku mabwiriza yo kugura impapuro z'isuku, ku buryo ku maduka yose yo mu gihugu hose, ku isoko rimwe ryahise haboneka impapuro ebyiri za 'Wallworths' n'impapuro imwe ya 'Kohl's'.
Nanone kandi, amaduka ya Aldi yashyizeho umunsi umwe, ni ukuvuga kuwa mbere.
Ibi bihano byo kugura byashyizwe nk'ubutumwa ku bibanza by'ingurane mu maduka n'amapaji yayo ya Facebook.
Hari amakuru avuga ko abaguzi bagiye babitekeraho kubera impungenge z'uburwayi bwa COVID-19 mu gihe abantu baba bakeneye kwicumbikira bonyine.
Ku wa gatatu, amaduka akomeye yitwa Wall Worth yemeje ko nta mpapuro z'isuku zigomba kujya mu ngo z'abantu, ku buryo buri kintu cyose cyakagombye kuba igizwe n'urupapuro rumwe.
Ayo mahinduka yaje nyuma y'ibihano byari byarafashwe n'amaduka ya Wall Worth ku ya 4 Werurwe na Koles ku ya 5 Werurwe byemereraga kugura impapuro enye gusa ku isoko.
Mu itangazo ry'itangazamakuru ryasohowe ku ya 8 Werurwe, Kalls yavuze ko nubwo hari amategeko agenga imikono ine, "amaduka menshi akomeje kugurisha ibyo afite byose mu gihe cy'isaha imwe nyuma yo kubakira", avuga ko ibyo basabye ari "bitigeze bibaho", kandi ko Aldi na yo mu butumwa yashyize kuri Facebook ku wa Kabiri yavuze ko ari "bitunguranye".
Umuvugizi wa Wal-Worth avuga ko mu cyumweru gishize, ibicuruzwa byariyongereye cyane.
Mu cyumweru gishize, i Canberra, i Costco yavuze ko abantu bemerewe kugura litiro ebyiri.
Kugira ngo bagabanye ikibazo cy'ibura, amaduka ya Kohl yasabye abaguzi bayo gupakira ibicuruzwa byinshi no kongera umuvuduko wo kubitanga, amaduka ya Wall Worth yasabye ibicuruzwa byinshi, mu gihe amaduka ya Aldi yafunguriye ibicuruzwa byayo ibicuruzwa bidasanzwe biteganyijwe kuwa gatatu w'ejo.
Umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi muri Ositaraliya, Russell Zimmerman, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa, ariko ko amategeko y'akarere agenga igihe cyo gutanga ibikamyo atuma ibyo bigorana.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'umusaruro bizamuka, kuko abaguzi bagerageza guhaza ibisabwa, n'ibitaramo byihariye bigabanuka.
Ku wa kabiri, amaduka ya Aldi yatangaje ko kubera ko ibicuruzwa byabonetse hakiri kare, amaduka amwe n'amwe atazashobora gutanga igitaramo cyo ku wa gatatu.
Dr. Mortimer, impuguke mu bucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi muri Kaminuza ya Queensland y'ikoranabuhanga, yavuze kuri News.com.au ko amaduka yuzuye buri joro.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'isuku ari ibintu byinshi, bituma umubare w'ibikoresho ugabanuka, kandi iyo zigurishijwe zose, zisigara ari ubusa ku mashami, bigatuma abantu bumva ko zibuze.
Nk'uko byavuzwe na Russell Zimmerman, dukurikije uko bivugwa na ABC News, "ab'amazu y'ubucuruzi ya Kohl's na Wal-Mart batekereza ko [iyo] ibicuruzwa byinshi biboneka ku mashuka, kandi ko [ibintu] nk'udupfunyika two mu bwiherero n'imiti yo guhumanya indwara bishobora kugurwa kandi bigatangwa mu buryo bwinshi, bishobora kugabanya ubwoba".
