Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe kandi abanduye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso.
Indwara ebyiri zikunze kugaragara ni umuriro (88%) n'umuhogo utose (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara cyane birimo umunaniro, gusohora mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (pellegrine), kubura impumuro, guhumeka nabi, ububabare bw'ingingo n'imisatsi, kuribwa mu muhogo, umutwe, kugira ubwoba, gusubiramo, kuvoma amaraso, igifu cyangwa uburibwe. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryemeza ko umuntu umwe kuri batandatu arwaye cyane kandi afite ikibazo cyo guhumeka.
Ikigo cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyashyize ibimenyetso byihutirwa mu guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu gatuza cyangwa guhindagurika, guhindagurika mu buryo butunguranye, kugorwa no gukanguka, ubururu bw'amaso cyangwa iminwa. Ubuvuzi bwihuse burasabwa niba ibi bimenyetso bibonetse.
