Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Tayilande ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byateguye guhungisha abaturage babyo.
Pakistani yatangaje ko nta muturage wayo n'umwe izirukana mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yavanye muri icyo gihugu abaturage 34 b'Abanyabrezili cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, hamwe n'Abanyapolonye bane, Umushina umwe n'Umuhinde.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'Ubuhinde bavuye mu ndege muri Polonye, aho indege ya Bresil yahagaze mbere yo gutangira urugendo rugana muri Bresil.
Abaturage ba Brazil bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, 39 bari mu ya kabiri yari ikodeshejwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bakuwe i Wuhan bajya ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Canada cya Trenton mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanaada 185 bari baturutse i Wuhan, yageze ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Canada i Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Ositaraliya bahungishije abaturage 277 ku ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare bajya mu kigo cyo gufungira ku kirwa cya Noheli, cyongeye gukoreshwa nk'ikigo cy'ihererekanya, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Ubwato bw'abimukira bwa Nouvelle-Zélande bwageze i Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare, kandi abagenzi babwo (harimo abantu baturutse muri Ositaraliya na Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Wanjapararawa mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gucyura Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bw'ubukerarugendo bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yageze i Trenton, Ontario, itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bakuwe mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye kuvana abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airlines yari yaraguzwe na guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yasubije abaturage 112 b'Abanyafurika y'Epfo.
Bakoze isuzuma ry'ubuzima mbere yo kugenda, maze abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus barekurwa kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo bagarutse gusa bafite ibipimo byabo by'ibizamini byagize ingaruka mbi.
Ibisubizo by'ibizamini byagaragaje ko Abanyafurika y'Epfo, barimo abakozi ba ndege, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bose bari bamaze iminsi 14 mu kato no kugenzurwa muri Ranch Resort, nta bwandu bafite.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad, Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri za kaminuza zo muri Amerika bashyize hamwe bohereze imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byanduye, bivugwa ko itsinda ry'abafatanyabikorwa bo mu karere ka Chicago bashoboye kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 tw'ubwoko bwa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Direct Relief, ifatanyije na FedEx, yohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi, birimo utwenda tw'amaboko n'imyambaro y'abakozi b'ibitaro, binyuze mu kiraro cy'ubutabazi bw'indege, ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika ku Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) mu rwego rwo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku nkingo no ku miti, ndetse no kurinda "abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Interaction yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 muri Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapuru yatangaje ko izohereza inkunga y'amadolari ya Amerika miliyoni 2.26 mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko izatangaza uturindantoki tw'ubuvuzi miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birimo udupfukamunwa 10,000, Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, ndetse n'ibindi by'ubufasha bw'amafaranga ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu bihugu byazahajwe. Nyuma y'uko ibintu byasubitswe mu Bushinwa, igihugu cyatangiye kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu bitandukanye byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'u Burusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje muri Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda aho byatangwaga n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza muri Panama ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 na respirateur eshanu.
U Buholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Tchèque byatangaje ko bitewe n'udupfukamunwa n'udupfunyika tw'ibizamini byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye mu Bushinwa udupfukamunwa 58.000 twakorewe mu Bushinwa twagenewe gupima coronavirus twari dufite ubuziranenge bwa 30%, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwo bwisubije mu Bushinwa udupfukamunwa 600.000 twari dufite inenge.
Ububiligi bwasubije inyuma udupfukamunwa 100,000 tudakoreshwa twitwaga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twari twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, ibice bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika byakiriye neza inkunga y'Ubushinwa. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubufasha mu bihe by'ibiza ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimiye imbaraga z'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa mu gucunga no guhashya icyorezo.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryagaragaje itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002 na 2004, aho abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga kuba barahungabanyije ibikorwa byo kwirinda no kugabanya ubwandu, n'ikibazo kiriho ubu, aho leta nkuru yatanze "amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo yirinde ubwoba mbere y'ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ibanze cyo gushyiraho itegeko ryo guhagarika uburyo bwo gutwara abantu mu mujyi wa Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS, Goodin Galya, yavuze ko nubwo "nta gushidikanya ko ari inama yatanzwe na OMS", ariko ko ari "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cyo kwiyemeza kugabanya icyorezo aho cyibasiwe cyane", avuga ko "bitigeze bibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko umuntu umwe ajya mu wundi hanze y'Ubushinwa, kandi umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukene bw'ubuzima rusange bw'isi yose (ICPIC), kikaba ari icya gatandatu mu bibazo by'ubukene bw'ubuzima rusange mpuzamahanga kuva icyo gikorwa cyatangira kwitabwaho mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya Ebola mu 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko iki cyorezo gifatwa nk'impanuka y'ubuzima mpuzamahanga kubera "ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abiciriritse bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
Mu gusubiza ku itegurwa ry'ibihano byo gutembera, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zibangamira ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "WHO idatanga inama yo kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari mu nkunga z'ingamba mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, ivuga ko hakenewe cyane gushyigikira ibyo bihugu "bitafite uburyo bwo gupima abantu banduye virusi, niyo yaba igaragaye".
Tedros kandi yagize amagambo avuga ko "imbaraga zacu zigereranywa n'imbaraga z'umuntu ufite intege nke muri twe" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kwishora mu bikorwa uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura amafaranga menshi nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, yise iyi ndwara COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres, yemeye gutanga "ubushobozi bw'umuryango w'abibumbye mu buryo bwose bwo gusubiza".
Ingaruka zabaye uko hashyizweho itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo, ryemerera guhuza igisubizo cyose cya ONU, kandi rizemerera OMS "kwita ku bisubizo by'ubuzima mu gihe ubunararibonye bw'izindi nzego bushobora kwifashishwa kumenya ingaruka rusange z'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere ry'icyorezo".
