Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'ubutabazi bw'ubuzima bw'ibanze muri OMS, mu itangazo yatanze, yatanze umuburo agira ati "iki ni ikigeragezo nyacyo kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: ni yo mpamvu tugomba kwitegura.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi mugomba kuyitegura", asaba ko hafatwa ingamba zo kuyirwanya zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi kurushaho".
Ryan yavuze kandi ko amakuru ariho adashobora kwemeza ko abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza bene ibyo bisobanura ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azafatwa n'iyi virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru yavuze ko OMS "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ibipimo biteye ubwoba by'ikwirakwira n'uburemere, n'ibipimo biteye impungenge byo kutagira icyo ikora". OMS yahuye n'ibitotezo bikomeye ku cyo yabonaga ko ari uburyo budahagije bwo guhangana n'icyorezo, harimo gutinda gutangaza ibyago by'indwara y'uburwayi bw'abaturage, no gushyira virusi mu byiciro by'icyorezo.
Mu bitabiriye ibikorwa by'urugomo harimo n'icyemezo cy'umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom cyo kwegura, cyashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 guhera ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere nyinshi mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu muri Loni zashimangiye ko uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bwose bwubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira bwo gufashwa mu kurokora ubuzima kandi ko leta ifite inshingano yo kubikora.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura amikoro cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba kuba impamvu yo kubarira itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bemeje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, harimo abafite ubumuga, abo mu moko mato mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abashyitsi, abatagira aho baba, abari mu mimerere mibi cyane, abafunzwe, impunzi n'andi matsinda adasobanutse akeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ya leta irimo gukemura ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage byatewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
OEC yatangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru arambuye kandi ku gihe ku bisubizo by'ingamba mu bihugu byo ku isi, ndetse n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku ngamba zo gushimangira uburyo bw'ubuzima n'ubukungu ku isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka z'ifungwa n'ibihano ku ngendo, umuyoboro wa digitale urimo igikoresho cyo gukurikirana politiki y'igihugu, kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bindi no koroshya igisubizo cy'isi yose cyo guhangana na coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'ibiro by'abaminisitiri by'Ubwongereza Michael Gove, na Edward Bolsonaro umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili, Jair Bolsonaro, kubera uburyo yakemuye icyorezo, cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei y'Ubushinwa.
Abayobozi benshi bo mu rwego rw'amashyaka menshi ya CPC birukanywe kubera uburyo bakiriye ibikorwa byo kwitarura abantu mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, mu kugaragaza ko batishimiye uko inzego za politiki zitabiriye iki cyorezo muri utwo duce.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo batekereza ko icyo gikorwa cyari kigamije kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa, Xi Jinping, uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bahitamo kwemera ibitekerezo by'ubuhotozi byavuzwe na Amerika cyangwa u Butaliyani ku bijyanye na COVID-19.
Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump bwa Amerika bwise coronavirus "virusi yo mu Bushinwa" cyangwa "virusi ya Wuhan", buvuga ko Ubushinwa "bwarashyize ahagaragara amakuru yatumye virusi ubu yabaye icyorezo ku isi irushaho kwiyongera", ibyo bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko ari amacakubiri "kandi [ko] bitesha [ubumenyi] ku kuba yananiwe gucunga neza iki cyorezo".
Daily Beast yabonye telegrafe ya leta ya Amerika isubiramo gahunda yo gutumanaho n'ibitangazamakuru by'ibanze byo mu kanama gashinzwe umutekano w'igihugu, ivuga mu buryo bw'amayeri ko "byose ari ibya Ubushinwa.
Twasabwe gushaka no gukwirakwiza ubwo butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama n'amateleviziyo. "Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imbaraga z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byugarijwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa by'ubucuruzi bwo kwamamaza kugira ngo bigire ingaruka ku isi.
Umukozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga muri EU, Josep Borrell, yaburiye ko hari "igice cya politiki kirimo urugamba rwo kugira uruhare binyuze mu bikorwa byo gukabya no gutanga".
Burrell kandi yagize ati "Ubushinwa burimo gushishikariza ubutumwa ko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ari umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe".
Ubushinwa bwasabye kandi Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, mu gihe bivugwa ko bwohereza imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Ibihano bya Amerika byabujije Jack Ma gutanga udupfukamunwa 100,000 muri Cuba ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika kandi bashinjwa kwimura imfashanyo zari zigenewe ibindi bihugu zikajya muri Amerika.
Hari kandi amakimbirane ajyanye n'udupfukamunwa yavuzwe mu bindi bihugu, nk'u Budage, Autriche, Suisse, Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe imashini amagana z'ubuhumekero zigenewe Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko EU idafite ubufatanye n'Ubutaliyani bwazahajwe na coronavirus.
Mauritsso Massari, ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yagize ati "Ubushinwa ni bwo bwitabiriye gusa ku rwego rw'ibihugu byombi.
Nta gushidikanya, ibi si ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'i Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kuvugana kuri telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yateguye ingabo z'Uburusiya kohereza abaganga ba gisirikare, imodoka zihariye zo kuvura, n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo "isoko rikomeye rya politiki" ritavuzwe izina, kivuga ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo z'Uburusiya "nta cyo zivuze cyangwa nta cyo zimariye u Butaliyani".
Uyu mushinjacyaha yashinje u Burusiya gutangiza igitero gikomeye cya "gipolitiki n'ibya dipolomasi".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, n'umunyamabanga w'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Ubutaliyani Luigi Di Maio bahakanye ibyo bitangazamakuru kandi bagaragaza ko bashimira.
Uburusiya kandi bwohereje indege itwara abantu n'ibintu byo kwa muganga muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "mu gufasha bagenzi be bo muri Amerika, [Putin] atekereza ko igihe ibigo by'ubuvuzi byo muri Amerika bizongera gukora, na byo bizabasha kubibasubiza bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu bya Baltique, "Guns 2020", ni imyitozo ikomeye cyane NATO izakora kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye.
Umunyamabanga mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament, Kate Hudson yanenze imyitozo ya Defenders 2020 agira ati: "Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ubuzima rusange kiriho, imyitozo ntabwo iteza akaga ubuzima bw'ingabo z'Amerika gusa n'ibihugu byinshi by'iburayi biyijyamo, ahubwo n'abaturage b'ibihugu bizayibamo". Guverinoma ya Irani yagize ingaruka zikomeye kuri virusi, aho abadepite bagera kuri makumyabiri barembye, hamwe n'abandi bantu 15 ba politiki ba kera cyangwa bariho.
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yanditse ibaruwa rusange ku bayobozi b'isi ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020 asaba ubufasha, avuga ko igihugu cye kirwana no kurwanya icyorezo cy'indwara kubera kutagira amahirwe yo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano bya Amerika byashyizweho kuri Iran. Icyorezo cyateje impaka muri Amerika kugirango cyemere politiki z'imibereho y'abaturage zikunzwe mu bindi bihugu bikize, harimo ubuvuzi busesuye, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango uhembwa, n'amafaranga menshi y'ubuzima rusange.
Abasesengura politiki batekereza ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku mahirwe ya Donald Trump yo kongera gutorwa mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu yo mu 2020. Imibanire ya dipolomasi hagati y'Ubuyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yangiritse kubera icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati y'igishuko kandi idashyize mu gaciro" y'Ubuyapani nyuma y'uko Ubuyapani butangaje ko umuntu wese uza aturutse muri Koreya y'Epfo azajya mu kato mu byumba bya leta mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage ba Koreya y'Epfo bari bafite impungenge ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yakiriye icyo kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon yahagarikwa kubera ko bavuga ko leta yakiriye nabi iki cyorezo cyangwa se ishimagiza igisubizo cyayo. Iki cyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byemera amategeko y'ibihe bidasanzwe mu rwego rwo guhangana nacyo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko bafite impungenge ko ibyo bishobora gutuma ubutegetsi bugira ububasha bukomeye.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yatoye yemerera minisitiri w'intebe, Viktor Orban, gutegeka ku buryo buhoraho, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko ndetse n'amatora no guhana abatangaga amakuru y'ibinyoma kuri virusi ndetse n'uburyo leta yakemuye iki kibazo.
Yashinjwe icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyateje ibibazo byinshi by'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa kubera ko ku isi hose hakoreshwa ibikoresho byinshi byo kurwanya icyorezo, kugura ibintu bitewe n'ubwoba, no guhagarika inganda n'ibikorwa by'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze imiburo ku bijyanye n'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi kubera ko abakiriya bifuza cyane kandi abaguzi batabasha kubikora.
Uturere twinshi kandi twabonye abantu bagura ibintu mu buryo bwo gutinya, bituma ibigega by'ibikoresho by'ibanze nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amacupa y'amazi biba bidafite ibicuruzwa bihagije, bituma habaho ubukene.
Uruganda rw'ikoranabuhanga rwamaganye cyane cyane ibitaramo byo gutumiza ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki.
Dukurikije uko umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, abivuga, ibisabwa ku bikoresho byo kwirinda bishobora kwiyongera inshuro 100.
Ibi byatumye ibiciro byiyongeraho inshuro zigera kuri makumyabiri ugereranyije n'igiciro gisanzwe kandi binatuma ibicuruzwa by'imiti bidatinze hagati y'amezi ane n'atandatu.
Nanone kandi, byateje ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku isi hose, kandi OMS itera inkunga ko ibyo bishobora gushyira mu kaga abakozi b'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, iki cyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi ba Diego babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Australia mu Bushinwa.
Uwo mwuga watumye amata y'impinja aba make mu maduka manini kandi nyuma yaho yabuzanywa na leta ya Ositaraliya. Nubwo COVID-19 yogeye cyane mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, kandi bikurikirwa n'ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibiribwa, uturere twombi twarokotse ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zafashwe n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko bw'ibikomoka ku mbuto z'ibinyabuzima zirinze ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa byitezwe mu Burayi ndetse no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Amajyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani, aho umusaruro w'ubuhinzi ari munini, ntiwagabanutse cyane, ariko ibiciro bishobora kuzamuka nk'uko byitezwe n'abahagarariye inganda.
Amashelfu y'ibiribwa yari yabaye ubusa by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa bari barimo barekura ibyangombwa by'inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyo kurya bihagije.
Mu Butaliyani hari amategeko nk'ayo asaba abahinzi b'ibiribwa kubika ibicuruzwa byabo mu gihe habaye ibyago nk'ibyo.
Ubushinwa bwumvise ingaruka z'ubukungu bw'isi: Nk'uko raporo y'itangazamakuru yo ku ya 16 Werurwe ibigaragaza, ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba zafashwe na leta zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi buciriritse bwahise bugabanukaho 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari ihuriro rikomeye ry'ubukungu n'inganda, byagaragaraga ko icyorezo cya virusi ari ikibazo gikomeye kandi kibangamiye umutekano w'ubukungu bw'isi.
Agatha Demaris wo mu kigo cy'ubutasi bw'ubukungu, yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhindagurika kugeza igihe habonetse ishusho nziza y'ibishobora kuvamo.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bahanga mu by'inganda batangaje ko ingaruka z'icyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kuzamuka kurusha iz'icyorezo cya SARS cyateye hagati ya 2002 na 2004.
Impuguke zo muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis, zigereranya ko urujya n'uruza rw'ibicuruzwa ku isi rwagize ingaruka zirenga miliyari 300 z'amadolari, zishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Raporo zivuga ko Opec yagize "ihungabana" nyuma y'igabanuka rikomeye ry'ibiciro by'ibikomoka kuri peteroli bitewe n'ibyifuzo bike by'Ubushinwa.
Amasoko y'imigabane ku isi yose yaragabanutse ku ya 24 Gashyantare kubera ubwiyongere bukabije bw'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge zikomeje kwiyongera ku cyorezo cya coronavirus, ibipimo byinshi by'imigabane ya Amerika, harimo Nasdaq-100, Standard & Poor's 500, na Dow Jones Industrial Average byanditse igabanuka ryabyo rinini kuva mu 2008, hamwe na Dow yagabanutseho amanota 1,191, ikaba ari ugugabanuka kwayo kwinshi kumunsi umwe kuva mu makuba y'imari mu 200708.
Ibipimo bitatu byasoje icyumweru bigabanutseho 10%.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scop Ratings GmbH yemeje indangamuntu y'Ubushinwa, ariko ikomeza kugenzura ko nta cyo izageraho.
Imicungire y'imigabane yongeye kumanuka kubera ubwoba bw'icyorezo cya Coronavirus, kandi igabanuka rikomeye ryabaye ku ya 16 Werurwe.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu buzahinduka.
