Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko ingendo z'indege nyinshi zahagaritswe kubera ko abenshi mu bari bayisabye bari bacye, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Kantais, mu gihe ikigo cy'indege cy'akarere k'u Bwongereza, Flybe cyarasenyutse.
