Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ko hari uburwayi buherutse cyangwa bukomeje.
Kugenzura abasirikare b'umubiri (antitoxicology) bikoreshwa mu gupima no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'umubiri w'umurwayi bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje ku buryo bitagomba gutangazwa cyangwa badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibipimo by'urupfu rw'iyo ndwara n'urwego rw'ubudahangarwa bw'itsinda mu baturage bishobora kumenyekana hashingiwe ku byavuye muri iki kizamini.
Kubera ko ibizamini ari bike, nta gihugu na kimwe mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020 cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku ikwirakwira rya virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze kigenzura abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini mu mibare y'ibipimo mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Iri tandukaniro rishobora kandi kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa kubera ubwandu bw'indwara, ishobora kuba yarakajijwe cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Imikorere ya polymerase ininterahamwe yo guhindura inyandiko (RT-PCR) ishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma ibipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe mu buryo butandukanye, harimo isuku y'umuhogo cyangwa ibipimo by'umwanda.
Ibisubizo ubusanzwe biboneka mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi ibiri.
Imiti ikoreshwa mu gupima mu muhogo ikoreshwa mu gupima mu gihe cy'icyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma yacyo, virusi ishobora kuva mu muhogo ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bagenzuwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, hashobora gufatwa ibipimo by'umuyoboro w'umwuka mu buryo bwimbitse hakoreshejwe catheter yo kwotsa cyangwa gukoresha umuti w'ikinya (plug).
Imwe mu miti ya mbere ya PCR yatangijwe muri Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 ikoresheje uburyo bwa polymerase instantaneous reverse transcription (RT-PCR), ikaba yarashyizeho urufatiro rw'udupaki 250,000 tw'ibizamini tugiye gutangwa n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwakoze ikizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020.Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo Kogenebiotech nacyo cyakoze ikigega cya SARS-CoV-2 cya PowerChek Coronavirus, gihuje n'imikoreshereze myiza ya kliniki kandi gishingiye kuri PCR ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni cyo kigo cya mbere cyabonye uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bw'impanuka (emergency use approval) na China National Medical Products Administration (NMAP) ku gikoresho cy'ubushakashatsi cya SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyatanze ikarita y'ubushakashatsi ya COVID-19 (COVID-2019) ishingiye kuri RT-PCR ku bigo by'ubushakashatsi by'ubuzima rusange binyuze mu kigo mpuzamahanga gishinzwe gutanga ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi.
Imwe mu ncuro eshatu z'ibizamini byagenewe ku mashini zishaje z'ibizamini byagize ingaruka zitagira iherezo kubera ibimenyetso bidakwiriye, kandi imwe mu ncuro z'ibizamini yatinze ku zindi muri CDC i Atlanta; ibyo byatumye gupima ibipimo biri munsi ya 100 ku munsi ku kigereranyo birangira neza muri Gashyantare 2020.
Ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri ntibyigeze byemezwa kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, kandi kugeza icyo gihe, leta n'ibigo by'ubushakashatsi bya leta ntibyari byemerewe gutangira gukora ibizamini.
Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyemeje iki gikorwa mu buryo bw'ubugenzuzi bw'imiti. Ibitaro by'ubucuruzi muri Amerika byatangiye gukora ibizamini mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko icyemezo cyo gupima COVID-19 gishingiye kuri RT-PCR kizaba cyamaze gushyirwa mu bikorwa mu gihugu hose.
Muri ubwo buryo, Quest Diagnostics yatangiye gutanga ibizamini bya COVID-19 mu gihugu hose guhera ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta bipimo by'ibanze byatangajwe; ibipimo bigomba gukusanywa kandi bigakorerwa mu buryo buhuje n'ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, Ikigo cya Leta cy'Ubushakashatsi mu Bumenyi bw'Urugero n'Ikoranabuhanga mu Buzima cyatangije ikigo cya Viktor kigakora ikizamini cya COVID-19.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, FHSY yanditseho ikizamini. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, byatangajwe ko Mayo Clinic yateguye ikizamini cyo gutahura ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Rush Diagnostics yahawe FDA kwemerwa ku kizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3.5 ku bwinshi, bigatuma imashini imwe ishobora gukora ibizamini hafi 4128 mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti (FDA) cyatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (EUA) kuri Abbott Laboratories gukora igerageza kuri Abbott m2000; FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya nk'urwo kuri Hologic, Lap Corp na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cifid yahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa nk'ubwo na FDA ku kibazo cy'igerageza rimara iminota 45.
FDA yemeje ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi gikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongerera ubushyuhe ADN aho gukoresha PCR.
Kubera ko bidasaba ko umuntu akomeza kugabanya ubushyuhe, ubu buryo bushobora kugaragaza ibisubizo byiza mu minota itarenze itanu, n'ibisubizo bibi mu minota 13.
Ubu muri Amerika hari ibyuma bigera ku 18,000, kandi Abbott ateganya kongera inganda kugira ngo akore ibizamini 50,000 ku munsi. Taiwan irimo no gukora ikizamini gikoresha umuti umwe gusa uhuza neza na poroteyine ya coronavirusi (N-protein) mu byiringiro byo gutanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza kuri 20 nk'uko bigenda ku bipimo bya rubagimpande.
