Ubushakashatsi bwakorewe mu mujyi wa Wuhan bugereranya PCR na CT ku nkomoko y'icyorezo kiriho, bwagaragaje ko CT irusha PCR ubushobozi bwo kumva, nubwo idasobanutse neza, kuko ibintu byinshi by'amashusho yayo bibangamira indwara z'ibihaha n'ibindi byiciro by'uburwayi.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika Gishinzwe Isesengura ry'Imiterere cyatangaje ko "CT scan idakwiye gukoreshwa mu gupima COVID-19 cyangwa ngo ifashwe nk'igenzura ry'ibanze ryo gusuzuma indwara". Muri Werurwe 2020, CDC yatanze inama yo gukoresha PCR mu isesengura ry'ibanze.
Igice cy'igisubizo cy'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya ubwandu gikubiyemo gukora insinga z'umubiri, harimo IgM na IgG.
Zishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima abantu mu gihe cy'iminsi 7 cyangwa nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, mu gupima ubushobozi bw'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara, no mu gihe cy'igenzura ry'abaturage. Igerageza rishobora gukorwa muri laboratwari z'ibanze (CLT) cyangwa hakoreshejwe ibizamini byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi (POCT).
Imashini zikorana n'abantu ku giti cyabo zifite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini mu mavuriro menshi, ariko uburyo zizaba ziboneka bizaterwa n'uko buri mashini izakora.
Muri ibizamini bikorera muri sitasiyo, hakoreshwa urugero rumwe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso, nubwo hashobora gukoreshwa ibipimo byinshi kugira ngo hakurikirwe ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara.
Ku bipimo byo mu bitaro, akenshi amaraso afatwa mu buryo bw'umuvuduko umwe.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR, intambwe yo kuvanaho ntabwo isabwa mbere yo gusuzuma. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, FDA yagaragaje abantu 29 batanze amakuru kuri Agency hakurikijwe ibisabwa bityo abo bantu bashobora gutanga ibyo bafite by'ibizamini by'umubiri.
Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, FDA yemeje ikigo kimwe gusa cy'ikigo cy'iperereza cyemewe n'amategeko. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics na Epitope Diagnostics bahawe ibyangombwa by'ibanze by'ibikoresho byabo by'igerageza, bishobora kugaragaza antibody za IgG na IgA mu maraso.
Igikorwa cyo gupima cyakozwe mu masaha make, kandi ni vuba cyane kurusha PCR isanzwe yo gupima ADN ya virusi.
Imyanya ndangagitsina akenshi ishobora kugaragara nyuma y'iminsi 14 y'ubwandu. Mu ntangiriro za Mata, Ubwongereza bwabonye ko ibikoresho byo gupima imyanya ndangagitsina byaguzwe bitari byiza bihagije ku buryo byakoreshwa.
Hong Kong yashyizeho gahunda aho abarwayi bakekwaho kwandura bashobora kuguma mu ngo zabo, "ishami ry'ubutabazi riha abarwayi uruzogi rw'icyitegererezo", bakata mu ruzogi, bakongera bakarufata nyuma y'igihe gito. Ikigo cy'ubwisungane mu kwivuza mu Bwongereza (National Health Service) cyatangaje ko kirimo kugerageza gahunda yo gupima abantu bakekwaho kwandura mu rugo, bityo bikirinda ibyago byo kwanduza abanduye igihe baje kwa muganga cyangwa gukenera kugenzura imodoka ikoreshwa. Iyo umuntu apimwe COVID-19 ku bantu bakekwaho indwara batiriwe bava mu modoka, umukozi w'ubuzima akuramo ingamba.
Ibigo byo gupima mu modoka muri Koreya y'Epfo byatumye bakora ibizamini byihuta kandi byuzuye ku isi. Mu Budage, Ishyirahamwe ry'abaganga bashinzwe ubwisungane mu kwivuza ku wa 2 Werurwe, ryavuze ko ryabashije gukora ibizamini bigera ku 12,000 ku munsi ku barwayi bavuye hanze kandi abantu 10,700 barageragejwe mu cyumweru gishize.
Ubukangurambaga bw'ubuzima bufata amafaranga mu gihe muganga yategetse ko hakorwa ikizamini.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi w'ikigo Robert Koch, Ubudage bufite ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 160.000 buri cyumweru.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, ibizamini byo gupima virusi mu modoka byatangiye gukoreshwa mu mijyi minini.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'ibizamini byose byakozwe mu Budage ntiwari uzwi, kuko ibyavuye mu bizamini byatangajwe ari byiza gusa.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwa laboratwari bwagaragaje ko guhera mu cyumweru cya 12/2020, ibipimo 483,295 byakorewe ibizamini kugeza mu mpera z'icyumweru cya 12/2020, ibipimo 33,491 (6.9%) byagize ingaruka nziza kuri SARS-CoV-2. Muri Isiraheli, abashakashatsi bo mu kigo cy'ubuvuzi cya Technion n'ibitaro bya Rambam bahimbye uburyo bwo gusuzuma ibizamini byafashwe ku barwayi 64 icyarimwe kandi bagakora ibizamini, bagakusanya ibizamini kandi ntibagire ibindi bizamini keretse igishushanyo cy'itsinda cyerekanye ko gifite ingaruka nziza. Muri Wuhan, BGI yafunguye ikigo cy'igihe gito cyo gupima byihuse muri iki gihe gifite isuku y'ububwiherero 2000 yitwa "Yan-Huo Eye" (mu cyongereza: Fire Eye) cyangwa "Fire Eye", ishobora gupima ibizamini birenga 5 000 muri 2020.
Mu gihe Wang Jian, washinze BGI, yari ayoboye imirimo y'ubwubatsi, kandi byatwaye iminsi 5, imikorere y'ububiko yagaragaje ko ubwandu muri Hubei bwari kuzamukaho 47% kandi ibiciro byo gushyirwa mu kato byari kuzikuba kabiri iyo ubushobozi bwo gukora ikizamini butaboneka.
Laboratwari ya Wuhan yahise ikurikirwa n'ibikoresho bya Huo-Yan i Shenzhen, Tianjin, Beijing, Shanghai no mu mijyi 12 yose yo mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 4 Werurwe 2020, umusaruro w'ibanze w'ibanze wageze ku bipimo 50,000 ku munsi. Origami Assays yasohoye ibishushanyo mbonera byuguruye kandi bitanga amakuru menshi bishobora gupima ibipimo 1122 by'umurwayi kugenzura COVID-19 ukoresheje ibizamini 93 gusa. Ibi bishushanyo mbonera byuzuye bishobora gukoreshwa mu ma laboratwari mato adakeneye ibikoresho by'imashini byo kuvura.
Muri Werurwe, kubura no kutagira ibikoresho bihagije by'ubushakashatsi byatumye habaho ikibazo cy'ibipimo byinshi mu Burayi, mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika.
Ibi byatumye abahanga bamwe na bamwe bagerageza gukora ibizamini byo gutegura ibipimo birimo gushyushya ibipimo kuri 98 ° C (208 ° F) iminota 5 kugirango basohoze genome ya RNA kugira ngo bakore ibindi bizamini. Ku ya 31 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko UAE iri ku isonga mu bihugu byo ku isi mu gupima coronavirus ku baturage bayo, kandi iri mu nzira yo kuzamura ibipimo kugirango bigere kuri benshi mu baturage.
Ni mu buryo bwo guhuza gukoresha ubushobozi bwo gupima mu modoka, no kugura ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cya Group 42 na BGI (kishingiye ku bigo byabo by'ubushakashatsi bw'ubutabazi "Huo-Yan" byo mu Bushinwa).
Iki kigo cyubatswe mu minsi 14, gishobora gukora ibizamini bya RT-PCR ibihumbi n'ibihumbi ku munsi, kikaba ari cyo kigo cya mbere ku isi gifite ubu bunini gikorera hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Uburyo butandukanye bwo gupima bugamije ibice bitandukanye by'imiterere ya virusi ya Corona bwakozwe mu Bushinwa, u Bufaransa, u Budage, Hong Kong, u Buyapani na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
OMS yemeje gahunda y'u Budage yo gukora ibikoresho byo kohereza mu bihugu bifite amikoro make kandi bidafite amikoro yo guhanga ibikoresho byabyo.
Igikorwa cyo mu Budage cyatangajwe ku ya 17 Mutarama 2020; porogaramu yashyizweho n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara ntiyabonekaga kugeza ku ya 28 Mutarama, bituma ibizamini biboneka muri Amerika bidindira. Ubushinwa na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika byahuye n'ibibazo bijyanye n'ukuntu ibikoresho byo gupima byari bifitiye icyizere mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, kandi ibyo bihugu byombi na Ositaraliya ntibyashoboye gutanga ibikoresho bihagije byo guhaza ibyifuzo no gukurikiza inama zo gukora ibizamini zatanzwe n'inzobere mu by'ubuzima.
Ku rundi ruhande, impuguke zivuga ko ibipimo byinshi byo muri Koreya y'Epfo byafashije mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus nshya.
Leta ya Koreya y'Epfo yongereye cyane ubushobozi bwo gupima mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi byigenga mu myaka myinshi.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, OMS yasabye ko gahunda zo gupima zihuzwa nk'umuti mwiza wo kugabanya iterambere ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19. Kwiyongera kw'ibisabwa byo gupima kubera ikwirakwira rya virusi byatumye ibihumbi amagana by'ibizamini byongerwa mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi byigenga byo muri Amerika, kandi ibicuruzwa by'imashini zo gupima no gupima byagabanutse.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko hari ibibazo mu buryo bw'ukuri mu bikoresho by'igerageza.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, hari "intege nke" mu bikoresho by'isuzuma byakozwe na CDC; hanyuma leta yakuyeho inzitizi z'ubutegetsi zatumaga iki kibazo kitajya mu isuzuma. Espagne yaguze ibikoresho by'isuzuma ku kigo cy'Ubushinwa Shenzhen Bioeasy Biotechnology Ltd, ariko isanga ibisubizo bitarimo ukuri.
Ikigo cyasobanuye ko ibisubizo bitari byo bishobora guterwa no kunanirwa gukusanya ibipimo cyangwa gukoresha nabi ibikoresho.
Minisiteri ya Espagne yatangaje ko izasubukura kugura ibikoresho bitanga ibisubizo bitari byo, ikabisimbuza ibindi bikoresho byo gupima bya Shenzhen Bioeasy. 80% by'ibikoresho byo gupima byaguze Repubulika ya Tchèque bivuye mu Bushinwa byatanze ibisubizo bitari byo. Slovakia yaguze ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.2 bivuye mu Bushinwa byagaragaye ko bidakwiriye.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Matovic yasabye ko bijugunywa mu ruzi rwa Danube. Prof. Ahmet Kara wo muri Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Turukiya yatangaje ko ibikoresho byo gupima byaguzwe na Turukiya bivuye mu Bushinwa bifite "ibipimo byinshi by'ikosa" kandi "byarangiye gukoreshwa". Ubwongereza nabwo bwaguze ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 3.5 bivuye mu Bushinwa ariko mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020 butangaza ko bitemewe.
Ibizamini, bikurikiwe no gushyirwa mu kato kw'abanduye no gukurikirana abahuye n'abanduye SARS-CoV-2, byagize ingaruka nziza.
Abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Fo, mu Butaliyani, aho abantu ba mbere bishwe na COVID-19 mu Butaliyani, bakoze ibizamini ku bantu bose bagera ku 3,400 incuro ebyiri, buri gihe bikaba byaratwaye iminsi igera ku icumi.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abantu bagaragaweho iki cyorezo nta bimenyetso bagaragaje, kandi abamaze kwandura bose baratoranyijwe.
Kubera ko abantu batemerewe kujya mu migi itandukanye, abanduye bashya baramaze kurandurwa.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2020 muri Singapore cyagize igipimo cyo kugabanuka cyane ugereranyije n'ibindi bihugu byateye imbere, ariko nta ngamba zikomeye nko gufunga amarestora n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi; binyuze mu gukurikirana cyane abahuye nacyo no gushyiraho ingamba ku ngendo z'imbere mu gihugu, gupima no kwihererana.
Ibikorwa byinshi byahagaritswe, kandi Singapore yatangiye gusaba abaturage kuguma mu ngo zabo ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko amashuri yongeye gufungura ku ya 23 Werurwe igihe yari yateganyijwe nyuma y'ikiruhuko.
Ibihugu byinshi na byo byagenzuye iki cyorezo binyuze mu gukurikirana cyane abahuye nacyo no gushyiraho amategeko yo kugabanya ingendo z'imbere mu gihugu, gupima no gushyirwa mu kato, ariko n'amabwiriza yo gufunga make, nk'uko bimeze muri Isilande na Koreya y'Epfo.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko ibihugu byakoze ibizamini byinshi ugereranyije n'iby'abantu bapfa, bifite umubare muto w'abapfa, wenda kubera ko ibyo bihugu bishobora kubona abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso na mba.
OMS isaba ibihugu bidafite ubushobozi bwo gupima cyangwa bifite ibigo by'ubushakashatsi byo mu gihugu bifite ubumenyi buke kuri COVID-19 kohereza ibipimo bitanu bya mbere by'indwara ya COVID-19 na 10 bya mbere by'indwara ya COVID-19 kuri kimwe mu bigo 16 byemewe na OMS kugira ngo byemeze ko ari byo byapimwe.
Muri za laboratwari 16 zemewe, 7 ziri muri Aziya, 5 ziri i Burayi, 2 muri Afurika, 1 muri Amerika ya Ruguru, na 1 muri Ositaraliya.
Mu mbonerahamwe ikurikira, umurongo "% y'ibizamini byagize umusaruro mwiza" ugira ingaruka ku buryo igihugu gikora ibizamini.
Igihugu kigenzura abantu bajyanywe mu bitaro gusa, kizaba gifite igipimo cy'abantu benshi bapimwe kurusha igihugu kigenzura abaturage bacyo bose, batagaragaza ibimenyetso cyangwa batabigaragaza, byose hamwe.
Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bizwi nka isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gusukura intoki mu rwego rwo gukuraho umwanda, ibinure, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi n'isabuni mu "bihe by'ingenzi" by'umunsi, bigabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, nk'ihosha n'ibicurane, byandura binyuze mu nzira y'umunwa.
Abantu bashobora no kurwara indwara z'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane, urugero, mu gihe batigeze bakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, amazuru cyangwa umunwa (ni ukuvuga mu mazuru).
Mu bihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa harimo: mbere na nyuma yo gusama, nyuma yo gusukura umwana cyangwa guhindura indabo, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere yo gutegura amafunguro cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko zikiri nto na nyuma yaho.
Iyo nta mazi n'isabune bihari, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje imicanga. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ritanga inama yo gukaraba intoki:
Mbere yo gutegura amafunguro, mu gihe cyo kuyateka na nyuma yayo.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Nyuma yo guhindura umwana indyamunyu cyangwa kumuhanagura nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero.
Nyuma yo gukaraba izuru, gukorora cyangwa gutera akabariro.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ibiryo byayo cyangwa imyanda yayo.
Isuku y'amaboko ni isuku ifitanye isano n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kwita ku barwayi bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi ni ukwitandukanya n'ibintu byateza indwara (indwara, virusi cyangwa ibindi bintu bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho by'imiti bishobora kwangiza cyangwa kurwara.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora mu biribwa cyangwa mu buvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, virusi ya corona n'izindi ndwara zitandura, gukumira indwara zandura zitera igifu, kugabanya ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero,
no kugabanya impfu z'abana babyarira mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2013 bwagaragaje ko imikoreshereze myiza yo gukaraba intoki ishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu barushaho gukura.
Mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'iseru ushobora kugabanuka mu gihe hakozwe impinduka zoroheje mu myitwarire, nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyo ngamba yoroheje ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bazize izi ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Ingamba zo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki zishobora kugabanya igifu ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, nk'uko amazi meza aba ari meza mu duce dukennye.
48% by'igabanuka ry'ibicurane bishobora kuba bifitanye isano no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda ibicurane n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (ARE) mu gihe imyitwarire ya automatike ikoreshwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Igicuri, kimwe mu ndwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero, ni cyo kintu cya mbere kihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, kigahitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Kurwara igifu n'igifu hamwe bituma abana bagera kuri miliyoni 3.5 bapfa buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero bishobora kurokora ubuzima kurusha urukingo cyangwa ubuvuzi ubwo ari bwo bwose, bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri icyorezo cy'indwara y'igifu, n'icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero mu buryo bukabije.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi bijyana n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku mu gihe cy'imiyoborere y'amazi n'isuku.
Gukaraba intoki kandi birinda indwara ya kanseri yandura binyuze mu guhura n'umuntu imbonankubone.
Ingaruka mbi yoroheje yo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora kwangiza uruhu kubera ko rukonja.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danemark mu 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cy'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'amaboko, bita eczema y'intoki cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, kandi bikunze kugaragara cyane cyane mu bakora mu by'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki cyane akenshi bifatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara y'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'uruhu: nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (gusiramura, gusama), nyuma yo gusukura umugongo w'umwana (guhindura indimu), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere/nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko itaragezweho.
Gukaraba intoki neza ni ngombwa no mu bindi bihe kugira ngo wirinde kwandura, nko mbere cyangwa nyuma yo kuvura igikomere cyangwa igikomere, nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa kwihanagura amazuru, nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa kuyikoraho, no nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, gukaraba intoki n'isabune biragabanuka.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo ingo 38.7% zikaraba intoki n'isabuni. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwerekanye ko Saudi Arabia ifite igipimo cyo hejuru kigereranywa na 97%, Amerika ikaba yegereye hagati na 77%, naho Ubushinwa bukaba bufite igipimo cyo hasi cya 23%. Ubu hari uburyo bwinshi bwo guhindura imyitwarire bwo kongera inyungu zo gukaraba intoki n'isabuni mu bihe bikenewe. Gukaraba intoki mu matsinda y'abana b'abanyeshuri mu bihe runaka by'umunsi ni bumwe mu buryo buhari mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere bwo gushyiraho umugenzo wo gukaraba intoki mu myitwarire y'abana.
"Gahunda y'Ubuzima bw'ibanze" yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa byinshi byo guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Kuvura udusimba kabiri mu mwaka, hamwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabuni, no gusukura amenyo buri munsi n'ifloride, ni byo by'ingenzi muri iyi gahunda y'igihugu.
Nk'uko byakozwe neza muri Indoneziya.
Gushyira isabune cyangwa imiti yo gusukura mu mazi bituma udukoko duto duto tuva ku ruhu.
Ingaruka nyamukuru z'isabune n'ibimesa ni ukugabanya ibyangiza gusandara, no kongera uburyo bwo gusama.
Amazi yonyine nta cyo amaze ku ruhu kuko ibinure na poroteyine, ari byo bikomoka ku butaka, ntibishobora kubora mu mazi.
Ariko kandi, amazi ahagije atuma habaho isuku.
Kubera ko isabune ya nyiramugengeri ishobora kongera gukoreshwa, ishobora kuba irimo za bagiteri z'ibyakoreshejwe mbere.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwagaragaje ko mikorobe zituruka ku isabune itavura, bwagaragaje ko zitagomba guturuka ku mazi kuko zikoreshwa nk'imashini yo gukaraba.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara kiravuga ko "gukoresha isabune y'amazi mu bikoresho bitakora ku isupu ari byiza".
Amasabune acuruza imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara, yakwirakwijwe cyane mu bakiriya bita ku buzima.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya igaragaza ko gukoresha imiti yica udukoko cyangwa imiti yica udukoko iba ari yo nzira nziza yo kurandura ibinyabuzima bidashobora kurwara imiti mu bidukikije.
Nyamara, isabune yica za bagiteri irimo imiti isanzwe yica za bagiteri nka triclosan, idakora ku bwoko bwinshi bw'ibinyabuzima.
Ku bw'ibyo, niba isabune ikoresha imiti igabanya ubukana bw'udukoko nta ngaruka igira ku bwoko bw'udukoko twirinda imiti igabanya ubukana bw'udukoko, ishobora kuba idakora neza nk'uko byatangajwe.
Uretse kugabanya stress yo ku mubiri no kurinda uruhu, ibishushanyo byakozwe bishobora kuba birimo aside (acide acétique, acide ascorbic, acide lactique) nk'umuyobozi wa acide, acide benzoïque ikora antibacterial n'ibindi byongera uruhu (cactus, vitamini, menethole, ibimera). Isesengura ryuzuye ryakozwe n'Ishuri ry'Ubuzima rusange rya Kaminuza ya Oregon ryerekana ko isabune isanzwe ifite ingaruka nziza nko ku isabune yabakiriya ifite triclosan mu kwirinda indwara no gukuraho mikorobe ku biganza.
Amazi ashyushye akwiriye gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ku buryo yica mikorobe.
Bakteriya zikura vuba cyane ku bushyuhe bw'umubiri (37°C).
Ariko kandi, amazi ashyushye n'isabuni bifite akamaro kurusha amazi akonje n'isabuni mu gukuraho amavuta asanzwe abungabunga umukungugu na za bagiteri.
Bitandukanye n'uko abantu benshi babibona, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta ngaruka bigira ku kugabanya mikorobe ku biganza.
Umunyoza intoki ni ikintu kitari gifite amazi cyo gusukura intoki.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, imiti yo guhanagura intoki itariho amazi kandi itavura (izitwa kandi ko ari amazi yo gukaraba intoki, umuti wo gukaraba intoki cyangwa imiti yica udukoko) yatangiye kwamamara.
Byinshi bishingiye kuri isopropyl alcohol cyangwa ethanol ihuriweho n'umuti utera uburemere nka carbomer (polymer ya acrylic acid) muri gel, cyangwa umusemburo nka glycerine mu mazi, cyangwa igifu kugirango bikore neza kandi bigabanyirize ingaruka zo kumeneka ziterwa na alcohol.
Kongeramo hydrogen peroxide yagabanyirijwe bituma ibikorwa byo kurwanya mikorobe byiyongera. Imiti yica mikorobe mu ntoki irimo nibura inzoga iri hagati ya 60 na 95%.
Inzitiramibu z'inzoga zikoreshwa mu gusokoza zangiza za bagiteri, za bagiteri zidakira imiti nyinshi (glycoma zidakira methisilin na za microbiomes zidakira vancomycin), igituntu, virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi itera SIDA, herpes, virusi itera indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, virusi z'imyanya y'ubuhumekero, iseru, ibicurane, ibicurane, no kurwara impiswi) na fungus.
Inzobere mu by'ubuvuzi z'inzoga zirimo inzoga 70% binyuze mu gusokoza zihitana 99,97% (igabanuka rya logarithmi rya 3.5, nk'igabanuka rya decibel 35) ya bagiteri ku biganza nyuma y'amasegonda 30 zishyiriweho na 99,99% kugeza kuri 99,999% (igabanuka rya logarithmi riri hagati ya 4 na 5) ya bagiteri ku biganza nyuma y'umunota 1 bashyizweho. Inzobere mu by'ubuvuzi z'amaboko zirakora cyane ku mikorobe kandi ntizikora cyane ku mikorobe zimwe na zimwe.
Imiti yica intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga nta cyo imaze na gato ku virusi za Norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ari na yo mpamvu ikunze gutera indwara y'igifu n'amaraso ituruka ku bwandu. Gukoresha umuti wica intoki cyangwa gusokoza inzoga bihagije bigomba gutuma intoki zombi zimira cyangwa zishyirwa mu mazi.
Gusuhagira imbere n'inyuma y'ibiganza no hagati y'intoki zose n'ibice by'ibiganza mu gihe cy'amasegonda agera kuri 30 kugeza amazi, ubuhuha cyangwa umutobe byumye.
Nanone kandi, ukwiriye gukaraba intoki neza, ukazikorakora ku mpande zombi. Ikigo cyo muri Amerika cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umuti wica udukoko, cyane cyane igihe ibiganza byanduye cyane.
Gukoresha cyane ibi bikoresho byanduza imyanda biterwa n'uburyo bworoshye bwo kubikoresha ndetse n'uburyo bwihuse bwo kurandura mikorobe; ariko, ntibikwiye kuba uburyo bwo gusukura intoki neza keretse amazi n'isabune bibaye bidahari.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yica udukoko tw'inzoga mu ntoki bishobora gutuma uruhu rukomera keretse iyo hari imvura cyangwa imiti yo guhumura uruhu cyangwa byombi.
Ingaruka z'inzoga ku kuntu uruhu rwumutse zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa zikarangira, hakoreshejwe glucerine cyangwa ibindi bintu byongera imvura cyangwa byombi.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga byagaragaje ko imiti yica udukoko ikoreshwa n'inzoga irimo amazi y'imvura ituma uruhu rudakara cyane kandi rukagira ikibazo cy'umwuma ugereranyije n'isabune cyangwa imiti yo guhanagura udukoko.
Indwara y'uruhu ituma umuntu agira ikibazo cyo kwisiga, indwara y'uruhu rw'amaboko, cyangwa kuba umuntu afite ikibazo cyo kurwara cyane inzoga cyangwa ibindi bintu byongera ku mazi yo gukaraba intoki.
Kuba abantu barwara indwara y'uruhu idakira cyane byahindutse ikintu gikomeye ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'amazi n'isabune.
Nubwo imiti yo guhanagura intoki itari ku mazi igira ingaruka nziza, ntiyica ibigize intoki ahubwo irazibuza.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, imiti yica udukoko idakora neza nk'isabune n'amazi mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, kuko indwara ziguma ku maboko.
Imikorere y'imiti itagira alukoro yo guhanagura intoki ishingiye cyane ku bikoresho n'imiterere yayo, kandi mu mateka, nta cyo yari imaze cyane ugereranyije n'imiti irimo alukoro, ishingiye ku gusokoza.
Vuba aha, ibimenyetso byagaragaje ko imiti ikoresha benzalkonium chloride igira ingaruka z'ubutabire kandi zirambye nk'indwara y'udukoko nyuma yo gukoreshwa, bitandukanye n'inzoga zigaragaza ko zigabanuka nyuma yo gukoreshwa kenshi, wenda kubera ibyiyumvo by'uruhu bigenda bihinduka.
Abantu benshi mu baturage badafite amikoro menshi ntibashobora kugura isabune, ahubwo bakoresha ivu cyangwa umukungugu.
Ivu cyangwa umukungugu bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha amazi yonyine, ariko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi kurusha isabune.
Hari impungenge ko niba umukungugu cyangwa ivu byandujwe n'udukoko duto, bishobora gutuma indwara ikwirakwira aho kugabanya.
Ivu na ryo, kimwe n'isabune, rikora nk'umwandazi kuko iyo rihuye n'amazi riba rifite umuti wa alkali.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatanze inama yo gukoresha ivu cyangwa umucanga mu gihe nta sabune ihari.
Uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki bwasabwe n'ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara, bukubiyemo intambwe zikurikira:
Ujye usukisha intoki amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje ava mu mugezi.
Gukoresha amazi acuncubuka ni byiza kuko amazi ari mu byumba bishobora kwanduza, kandi ku gihe kimwe ubushyuhe bw'amazi ntibugaragara ko hari icyo butwaye.
Kora isupu ku biganza, ubyuhagire isabune nyinshi, ukoreshe isupu ku mugongo, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'amano.
Sabune ikura mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakunda gukaraba intoki neza iyo bakoresheje isabune aho gukoresha amazi gusa.
Jya usama nibura amasegonda 20.
Gusiga bituma habaho imvune, bifasha gukura mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi kumara igihe kirekire cyane usuka mikorobe nyinshi.
Jya usukura neza amazi atemba.
Gukaraba intoki mu kibindi bishobora kongera kwanduza intoki.
Ujye uyuma ukoresheje agatambaro gashya cyangwa uyeke yumye mu kirere.
Ibiganza byumye kandi byumye birongera kwandura byoroshye. Ibice bikunze kwirengagizwa ni ikiganza cy'iburyo, ikiganza, hagati y'intoki, no munsi y'amano.
Inzara z'ibihimba by'umubiri n'amabara y'ibirenge ashobora kuba arimo udukoko duto.
Akenshi, gukoresha umuti urimo amazi meza mu ntoki ni byiza kugira ngo ubarinde gukonja, kuko iyo uruhu rukomeye rushobora kwangiza, bityo rukaba rwongera ibyago byo kwandura.
Amahitamo atandukanye y'igiciro gito ashobora gutangwa kugirango borohereze abantu gukaraba intoki mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere, aho amazi yo mu musarani cyangwa isabune cyangwa byombi bitaraboneka, nko kuvoma amazi mu nkono imurika cyangwa ikora imyobo ikwiriye, no/cyangwa gukoresha imyanda niba ari ngombwa. Mu duce dufite amazi make (urugero amashuri cyangwa uduce two mu cyaro mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari ibisubizo byo kugabanya ikoreshwa ry'amazi, nka "Tippi faucet" n'ibindi bintu byoroshye.
Tappi ni uburyo bworoheje bukoresha urwabya rwisunze umugozi, n'ukuboko kw'ikirenge kugenzura kugira ngo usuke amazi make ku biganza n'isabune.
Kumesa intoki neza ni igice cy'ingenzi mu gusukura intoki, ariko hari impaka ku buryo bwiza bwo kuzimya mu bwiherero rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera bugaragaza ko udupfukamunwa tw'impapuro ari two dufite ubuzima bwiza kurusha utwuma two koza intoki dukoreshwa mu bwiherero bwinshi.
Mu 2008, Kaminuza ya Westminster i Londres yakoze ubushakashatsi, bwatangijwe n'ikigo cy'u Burayi cy'imyenda ku bijyanye n'inganda z'impapuro z'ibyatsi, bugereranya isuku itanga impapuro z'ibyatsi, imashini zimesa intoki n'umwuka ushyushye, n'imashini zimesa intoki n'umwuka ushyushye.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzumesa mu buryo bw'umwuka ushyushye, umubare w'udukoko muri rusange wiyongereye ku kigereranyo cya 194% ku ntoki no ku kiganza cya 254%.
Kumesa ukoresheje umwumazi w'umwuka wa jet byongereye umubare rusange wa bagiteri ku ntoki ku kigero cya 42% no ku rutoki ku kigero cya 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki n'umwenda w'impapuro, umubare w'udukoko muri rusange ku kigereranyo ku ntoki ugabanutseho 76% no ku rutugu ku kigereranyo cya 77%. Abahanga bakoze ibizamini kugira ngo barebe niba hari ibyago byo kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'aho ubwiherero buba bitewe n'uburyo bw'umwuko.
Umwumazi w'umwuka wa jet, usohora umwuka hanze y'ikigo ku muvuduko ushobora kugera kuri 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), ushobora guhumeka mikorobi mu ntoki no mu bikoresho, kandi ushobora kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'aho ubwiherero buba mu ntera ya metero 2.
Gukoresha umwumazi w'umwuka ushyushye, bikwirakwiza mikorobe mu ntera ya metero 0.25 uvuye ku umwumazi.
Mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt bwagenzuye uburyo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki.
Dore impinduka zigaragara mu mubare w'indwara nyuma yo kumesa intoki:
Hari ababikora batandukanye, kandi bagereranya ibyo bikoresho n'ibikoresho byo kumesa.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje udupfukamunwa twanduza intoki ni ubundi buryo bwo gukora mu gihe cy'ingendo kuko nta isabune n'amazi biboneka.
Ikimonyo cyo ku maboko kigomba kuba kirimo nibura 60% bya alukoro.
Gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi byabaye itegeko igihe kirekire nyuma yuko umuganga w'umunya-Hongiriya Agnats Semmelweis avumbuye (mu 1846) ko ari ingirakamaro mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bitanga inyandiko zigaragaza ko abakozi b'ibitaro bagomba gukaraba intoki iyo bibagiwe.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukoresha ibiyobyabwenge byagabanyije ubukana bw'indwara.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi bigomba kumara nibura amasegonda 15, hakoreshejwe isabune nyinshi, amazi cyangwa umutobe wo gusokoza no gusokoza buri gice cy'intoki.
Amaboko agomba gusama, intoki zikagongana.
Niba hari umwanda munsi y'amano, ushobora gukoresha umudari ufite imisatsi migufi kugira ngo uwukureho.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuguma mu mazi yo ku ntoki, ni ngombwa ko uzisukura neza kandi ukazimanika n'umwenda mwiza.
Nyuma yo kumesa, ugomba gukoresha agatambaro ko mu rupapuro kugira ngo ufunze amazi (kandi ufungure urugi urwo ari rwo rwose niba ari ngombwa).
Ibi birinda imyanda y'amaboko kongera kuva kuri ibyo bisenge.
Gukaraba intoki mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bigamije gukuraho udukoko dutera indwara ("mikorobe") no kwirinda ko twandura.
Ikinyamakuru cy'ubuvuzi cyitwa New England Journal of Medicine kivuga ko kudakaraba intoki bikiri ku rwego rutabyemewe mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, abaganga benshi bibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bigatuma mikorobe zitwara.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza n'ibindi bikorwa byoroheje bishobora kugabanya ubwandu bw'amaraso bufitanye isano na kateteri ku kigero cya 66 ku ijana. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasohoye ikinyamakuru kigaragaza uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki no kuzisiga mu nzego z'ubuzima.
Inyandiko y'ibikubiye mu mabwiriza y'isuku y'amaboko yatanzwe n'iryo shyirahamwe ishobora no kuboneka ku rubuga rwayo, aho abantu bashobora kuyitangira ibitekerezo.
Whitby n'abandi bakoze ubushakashatsi ku birebana n'ibyo.
Imashini z'ubucuruzi zishobora gupima no kugenzura isuku y'amaboko, niba ari ngombwa kugaragaza ko yubahirije amategeko.
OMS ifite "Iminsi itanu yo gukaraba intoki":
Nyuma yo guhura n'amaraso/amazi yo mu mubiri
Mbere yo gukora igikorwa cyo gupima,
Nyuma yo kwita ku barwayi. Kongeramo imiti yica mu isabune ("ubuvuzi" cyangwa "ubuvuzi bw'udukoko) byongera ikintu cyica ku gikoresho cyo gukaraba intoki.
Iki kintu cyo kwica gishobora kwifuzwa mbere yo kubagwa cyangwa ahantu hari ibifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya imiti bita antibiyotike. Iyo umuntu "asukuye" ukuboko kwe kugira ngo akore ubuvuzi, bisaba kuba afite akuma gashobora gufungurwa no gufungwa adakoresheje amaboko, umuti wa chlorhexidine cyangwa iodine, utwuma twanduye two kumesa amaboko nyuma yo gukaraba, agashashi k'ubuvuzi kanduye, n'ikindi gikoresho kanduye cyo gusukura munsi y'amano.
Ibishushanyo byose by'imirimbo bigomba gukurwamo.
Iki gikorwa gisaba ko umuntu yoza intoki n'ibiganza kugeza ku nkokora, akenshi mu minota 2 kugeza kuri 6.
Si ngombwa ko ukarabe igihe kirekire (iminota 10).
Iyo usukura intoki, ugomba kwirinda ko amazi ava mu maboko yawe ajya mu maboko.
Iyo umaze gukaraba intoki, usukura intoki ukoresheje umwenda utagira icyo ukora, hanyuma ukambara umwenda w'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo uhagarike ikwirakwira ry'udukoko, ni byiza ko ukaraba intoki cyangwa ukoresha umuti wica udukoko mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
