Gucunga ibyago bya COVID-19 ku kazi
Gucunga ibyago bya COVID-19 mu kazi ni ugushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo gucunga ibyago mu kwirinda indwara ya koronavirusi ya 2019 (COVID-19).
Gucunga neza ibyago mu kazi bishingiye ku kazi n'inshingano, hashingiwe ku gusuzuma ibyago bituruka ku isoko, uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), akazi gashobora guteza ibyago byinshi gafite ingaruka nke ku bantu benshi no ku bandi bakorana, aho hagirwa inama yo gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo gukaraba intoki no gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo barwaye, gukurikiza imyitwarire yo gukorora no kohereza akayaga, no gukomeza ibikorwa bisanzwe byo gusukura no guhumanya aho bakorera.
Mu kazi gashobora guteza ibyago byinshi harimo akazi gashobora kuba gasaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegera abantu batazwi ko barwaye cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'ubwandu bukomeje mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri ibyo harimo abakozi bagiranaga n'abantu benshi nk'uko bigenda ku mashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo myinshi, ndetse no mu maduka acuruza ibintu mu buryo bunini.
Ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago by'iri tsinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, zirimo guhumeka ukoresheje imashini z'umwuka zikora neza, guhagarika gusinzira no gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwirinda mu gihe uhuye n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
Ikigo gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi kivuga ko abakozi bakora mu by'ubuzima n'abashinzwe kwita ku bantu bapfuye, bahura n'umuntu uzwiho cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19, bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, ibyo bikaba byongera ibyago byo kwandura cyane iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo guhumeka umwuka, cyangwa bakorakoranya ibipimo by'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19.
Ibipimo bikwiye byo kugenzura ibyago by'abo bakozi birimo ibipimo bya tekiniki nk'ibyumba byo guhumeka by'umuvuduko muke, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bikwiye akazi.
