Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) risaba ko abarwayi baza mu gihugu bashyirwa mu byumba by'indembe bishingiye ku kuba bakekwaho COVID-19. Uretse ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi, ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi bwemeza ko abantu bakorera ku birometero 6 uvuye ku barwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho SARS-CoV-2, n'abakora ibikorwa byo guhumeka umwuka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, udupfukamunwa dufite isuku ya N95 yemewe n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Umutekano n'Ubuzima mu Mwuga, cyangwa udupfukamunwa tw'ubwiza, tugomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'igikorwa cy'ubwirinzi bw'ubuhumekero bwanditse, gikubiyemo gupima imiterere, ubushobozi, amahugurwa n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi.
Ubundi bwoko bw'ibikoresho byo guhumeka bishobora gutanga uburinzi bwinshi no kunoza imiterere y'uburuhukiro bw'abakozi. OMS ntidushishikariza gukoresha ibipimo, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero aho kwanduzwa n'amazi yo mu mubiri.
OMS itera inkunga abakozi bakora ibizamini byo kwa muganga gukoresha udupfukamunwa gusa igihe binjiye mu gihugu.
Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero ku barwayi ba COVID-19, babitaho cyangwa babimurira ahandi nta buryo bwo guhumeka, OMS itera inkunga yo gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'abapima, indorerwamo, udukingirizo tw'amaso, udupfukamunwa n'utuboko.
Iyo hakozwe igikorwa cyo kuvura umwuka, agapfukamunwa gasimbuzwa agapfukamunwa ka N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ibikoresho byo kwirinda kwirinda ku isi yose bidahagije, OMS irasaba kugabanya ikenerwa ry'ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku buryo bwo kuvura ukiri kure, inzitizi z'iby'umubiri nk'amadirishya abonerana, yemerera gusa abashinzwe kwita ku barwayi kwinjira mu cyumba kirimo umurwayi ufite COVID-19, bakoresha ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku buryo bw'umubiri gusa bikenewe mu kazi runaka, gukomeza gukoresha agapfukamunwa kamwe gusa kandi nta kindi gihe cy'igihe kirekire mu gihe bita ku barwayi benshi bafite uburwayi bumwe, no kugenzura no guhuza uruzitiro rw'ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku buryo bw'umubiri, mu gihe bakoresha udupfukamunwa ku bantu badafite ibimenyetso.
