Ingingo ya ACE2 ifata ku gice cy'inyuma (urwiherero) rw'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
Angiotensin-2 converting enzyme (ACE) ikumira ibikorwa bya angiotensin-transforming enzyme (ACE) igabanya ingano ya angiotensin 2 kandi igatuma angiotensin (1-7) yiyongera; bigatuma iba umuti wizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima n'amaraso. Ni na yo nzira yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo zimwe na zimwe za virusi z'umugongo.
Ubwoko bwa muntu bwa enzyme akenshi buvugwa nka hACE2.
Ingingo ya angiotensin 2 ni ingirabuzimafatizo ya zinc iri ku rwego rw'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu nda n'izindi.
Poroteyine ya angiotensin 2 ifite enzyme ya transducer mu bwoko bwa peptidase M2 ifite amino end, hamwe na colectrine carboxyl end carrier ya amino acides y'impyiko.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ni poroteyine y'uruhu imwe yo mu bwoko bwa 1, ifite za récepteurs za enzymes zikora ziri ku buso bw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha n'izindi ngingo.
Igice cyo hanze y'urwego rw'ingirabuzimafatizo cy'indwara ya angiotensin 2 gica mu gice cy'urwego rw'urwego rw'urusobe rw'umubiri n'indwara yitwa shidases, bigatuma poroteyine ishira mu maraso, ikagenda mu maraso.
Ingingo ihindura angiotensin 2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi z'umubiri: ifatanye n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwoko 2 mu bihaha, mu ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu mara mato, mu ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu mitsi n'imitsi, ndetse no mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umusatsi zitoshye mu rukuta rw'imitsi mu ngingo nyinshi.
ADN yitwa RNA, ari na yo ituma habaho ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin 2, iboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'imbere mu gatuza no mu gice cy'ubwonko.
Imikorere y'ingenzi ya angiotensin-2 ni ugukora nk'igihinduranya angiotensin.
Ingingo ihindura angiotensin ituma habaho ihinduka rya angiotensin 1 mu angiotensin 2 ifata imitsi y'amaraso.
Mu buryo bunyuranye, ingirabuzima fatizo ihindura angiotensin 2 itandukanya karuboksili irimo amino acide phenylalanine na angiotensin 2 (aspartite-arginine-valine-tyrosine-isoleucine-histidine-brolin-phenylalanine) maze ikayihindura ingirabuzima fatizo ihindura angiotensin (1-7), (histidine-aspartite-arginine-phenylalanine-tyrosine-isoleucine-histidine-brolin-phenylalanine).
Ingingo ihindura angiotensin 2 yigabanyamo ibindi bice byinshi birimo [des-arginine9] - bradykinin, aplin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, na gerlin.
Ingingo ihindura angiotensin 2 kandi itegeka uruhu rw'umuvuduko wa SLC6A19, kandi igira uruhare muri Hartten's syndrome.
Ingingo ihindura angiotensin 2, nk'indwara y'uruhu, ni yo nzira y'ibanze yo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za virusi zimwe na zimwe z'umwimerere, zirimo koronavirusi ya NL63, SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS), SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 n'urusobe rwa enzymatic ya angiotensin 2 ku mbuga z'ingirabuzimafatizo bituma habaho kwisanzura kwa sellulaire, virusi n'iyo enzymate bigasohoka mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Ubu buryo bwo kwinjiza bukenera ko poroteyine S ihindurwa na poroteyine ya protease mu gice cy'urusobe, Serin2 ya nyirayo, ikomeje kugeragezwa nk'umuti ushobora gukoreshwa. Ibi bituma bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya urugero rwa enzyme ihindura angiotensin 2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
Ariko, imiryango myinshi n'imiryango yigenga, ivuga ko hakwiye gukomeza gukoreshwa imiti isanzwe ya angiotensin-converting enzyme inhibitors, hamwe n'imiti igabanya ingufu za angiotensin.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu buryo bufite gahunda no gusesengura byahindutse byasohotse ku ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 byagaragaje ko "gukoresha angiotensin-converting enzyme inhibitors byari bifitanye isano no kugabanya cyane ibyago byo kurwara ibicurane bya pumu ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'itsinda ry'ibanze".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibihaha byagabanutse mu barwayi bahabwa imiti igabanya imikorere ya angiotensin, kandi bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara iyi ndwara, cyane cyane abafite indwara y'ibihaha cyangwa umutima udakora neza.
Gukoresha imiti igabanya imyuka itera imyuka yitwa angiotensin transfusion inhibitors byagabanyije umubare w'abapfa bishwe n'umusonga, nubwo ibyo byagize ingaruka mbi ugereranyije n'ibyago byo kurwara umusonga muri rusange".
Umuntu ahindura angiotensin 2 (rhACE2) byitezwe ko ari uburyo bushya bwo kuvura uburwayi bw'ibihaha. Byagaragaye ko bufasha mu kuvura indwara z'ibihaha, ndetse no kongera umwuka mwinshi mu ngurube zifite indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye iseseme.
Ingingo ya kabiri y'ubuzima bwa angiotensin 2 ni amasaha agera kuri 10, mu gihe itangira gukora nyuma y'iminota 30, ndetse ikomeza gukora (igihe cy'amasaha) kugeza amasaha 24.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko angiotensin-2 converting enzyme ishobora kuba umuti uhebuje ku bantu bafite kudahanganira imiti gakondo ya angiotensin-systemic inhibitors (RAS inhibitors), no ku ndwara zifitanye isano n'umubare munini wa angiotensin-2 mu maraso. Hari ibizamini byo kwa muganga biri gukorwa, ku ngaruka zo guterwa angiotensin-2 converting enzyme mu kuvura indwara y'ubuhumekero bukabije.
