Abantu benshi bagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye n'ibanga, cyane cyane ku buryo bwo gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu baba.
Ibindi byagufasha kudahungabanya ubuzima bwite harimo gukoresha utwuma twa Bluetooth mu gufata amakuru y'uko uri hafi y'izindi telefoni zigendanwa.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko byashyize hamwe imikorere ishyigikira izi porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth, mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu z'imikorere ya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay bashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bamenya niba barahuye n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Ni porogaramu ikoreshwa n'abantu mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, abantu bakoresha porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga mu by'ikoranabuhanga cyateguye iyi porogaramu, irajya hanze nk'ifunguye kandi igiye gushyikirizwa leta. Macedonia ya Ruguru yatangije porogaramu ya "StopKorona", porogaramu ishingiye kuri Bluetooth ikoresha gukurikirana guhura kw'abantu bashobora kuba baranduye no gutanga ibisubizo byihuse ku bategetsi b'ubuzima.
Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga ifatanyije na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima, ni bo bakoze iyi porogaramu.
Ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari ikiri gutegereza kwemerwa n'ububiko bwa Google Play na App Store ya Apple.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu bari mu nzira y'amajyambere, ishobora kuba iboneka mu byumweru bike. Ireland n'u Bufaransa bitegura gushyiraho porogaramu nk'iyo, yitwa "StopCovid".
Australia na New Zealand byombi birimo gutekereza ku gukora porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether yatangijwe na Singapore, ndetse na BlueTress.Then.Russia irashaka gushyiraho porogaramu ikoresha virtual geo-periphery ku barwayi bagaragaweho COVID-19 baturutse i Moscou, igamije kubemeza ko batava mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ibibazo byinshi bishobora kubaho mu mikorere ishingiye ku porogaramu, harimo ibyiza by'ibinyoma no kutagira ingaruka nziza mu gihe porogaramu zikoreshwa mu gice gito cy'abaturage.
Kugira ngo Apple ibashe guhangana n'impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry'ibikorwa bya Coronavirus biyobya cyangwa byangiza, yashyizeho imipaka ku byiciro by'imiryango ishobora kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na Coronavirus yayo ku bubiko bwayo; aho yagenewe gusa imiryango "yemewe" cyangwa indi izwi neza.
Google na Amazon byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashyigikira ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka z'ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi by'abantu benshi biterwa no gukoresha porogaramu za Coronavirus, cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'uko ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi byakozwe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus bizakurwaho igihe cyose akaga kaba karangiye.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura bugabanywa.
Amashyirahamwe yatangaje kandi ibintu umunani bisabwa mu mishinga ya leta:
Igenzura rigomba kuba "ryemewe n'amategeko, rikenewe kandi rifite igipimo";
Ihererekanya ry'ibikorwa byo kugenzura no kugenzura rigomba kuba rikubiyemo ingingo zerekeye igihe cyo kubireka;
Gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba mu rwego rwo kwirinda COVID-19 gusa;
Umutekano w'amakuru n'ibanga ry'abo ayo makuru akesha bigomba kurindwa kandi bikagaragazwa ko bifite umutekano bishingiye ku bimenyetso;
Igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga rigomba kwirinda ivangura n'ivangura;
Gushyiraho amakuru ku bantu batandukanye bigomba kuba byemejwe n'amategeko;
Ibikoresho byo kurinda ikoreshwa nabi n'uburenganzira bw'abaturage mu guhangana n'ikoreshwa nabi bigomba kuboneka;
"Kugira uruhare mu buryo bukomeye" by'abafite "impamvu" bose, harimo impuguke mu by'ubuzima rusange n'amatsinda aciriritse, birakenewe. Ikigo cy'ubudage cyitwa Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na Reporters sans frontières (RSF) na byo byasohoye urutonde rw'ibisobanuro.
Umugambi uteganyijwe wa Google/Apple ugamije gukemura ikibazo cy'ubugenzuzi buhoraho binyuze mu gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana muri sisitemu zikora ibikoresho iyo bitakiri ngombwa.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byakoresheje uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho umuntu ari hakoreshejwe imbuga nkoranyambaga aho gukoresha porogaramu, bituma badakenera gukuramo porogaramu kandi bigatuma bashobora kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Israel, abayobozi bashyizeho uburyo bwo gukurikirana amakuru hakoreshejwe imiyoboro.
Ariko ibisubizo bishingiye ku mbuga bifite ubushobozi bwo kubona amakuru y'ibanze y'ahantu hari ibibazo bikomeye bishobora kuvuka bijyanye n'ibanga.
Ariko, ntabwo sisitemu zose zifite seriveri z'ibanze zikeneye kubona amakuru y'ahantu bwite; hari uburyo bwinshi bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite bwashyizweho bukoresha seriveri z'ibanze gusa mu itumanaho hagati yabo (reba igice gikurikira hepfo).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, abayobozi bakoresheje uburyo butari bushingiye ku porogaramu kugira ngo bakore ibikorwa byo gukurikirana abo bahuye.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu ikora amakuru yo gukurikirana aturutse ahantu hatandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'amakuru y'ibikorwa by'amakarita, kandi ikoresha ayo makuru yo kohereza imenyesha binyuze mu butumwa bugufi ku bantu bashobora kuba banduye.
Uretse gukoresha aya makuru kugira ngo hatangire gutangazwa abashaka kuyakoresha, leta yashyizeho uburyo bwo gutanga amakuru y'aho umuntu ari, byemewe n'ihinduka rikomeye ry'amategeko agenga ubuzima bwite bw'abantu nyuma y'icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyateje indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati.
Aya makuru aboneka ku mugaragaro binyuze muri porogaramu nyinshi na interineti. Ibihugu, birimo n'u Budage, byatekereje gukoresha uburyo bw'ibanze n'ubw'ibanga.
Ku itariki ya 6 Mata 2020, nta bisobanuro by'inyongera by'ibyo byabaye.
Gukurikirana abahuza bubahiriza ubuzima bwite ni igitekerezo cyakozwe kandi kigira ingaruka nziza kandi gishyigikiwe n'ibitabo bikomeye by'ubushakashatsi byatangiranye n'umwaka wa 2013. Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'abahanga arenga icumi yakoze ubushakashatsi ku bisubizo bihuza n'ibanga, nk'imbaraga nke za Bluetooth (PLE) zo gufata hafi umukoresha ku zindi telefoni zigendanwa.
Nyamara, BEPB-PT yari imbaraga ihuriweho ifite uburyo bwigenga n'ubw'ibanze, ntabwo ari protocole imwe. Imigambi ishingiye ku bwisanzure ikubiyemo gukurikirana uburyo bwo gutandukanya amakuru (DPBT/DPT-3T), imibare y'imishyikirano (TCN, yahoze yitwa imibare y'ibiganiro, CNE), protocols zisuzumye ubuzima bwite, uburyo bwo gukurikirana abanduye binyuze mu bikoresho bigendanwa (PACT) n'ibindi.
Muri ayo mabwiriza, amakuru y'umuntu ku giti cye ntava mu gikoresho, kandi ibikorwa byose byo guhuza bibaho ku gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'ibanga rya MIT Media Lab ryakoraga ku ikoranabuhanga rya SafePaths, urubuga rwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga rikingira ubuzima bwite mu gukusanya amakuru y'ahantu cyangwa inzira z'umuhanda no kuyakoresha mu gukurikirana ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu cyegeranyo cyiswe "Ubuso bubi bwa porogaramu: Kugumana ubuzima bwite muri iki cyorezo" cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Urubuga rwa SafeTrace rwa Enigma MPC, isosiyete ikora ikoranabuhanga ry'ibanga na yo yaturutse muri MIT Media Lab, ni ikindi gikorwa nk'icyo.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho bifite umutekano kugira ngo abakoresha bashobore gusangira amakuru y'aho bari n'amakuru y'ubuzima n'abandi bakoresha n'abayobozi batitaye ku bwisanzure bw'amakuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, Ishyirahamwe ryo gukurikirana umubare w'abamenyeshamakuru ku isi ryashinzwe n'amatsinda yibanda ku buryo bwari bumeze kimwe kandi budahuza cyane, hagamijwe kugabanya itandukaniro no gutuma interineti ihinduka ku isi hose hagati yo gukurikirana no gutanga amakuru, ikintu cy'ingenzi cyo kugera ku ikoreshwa ryinshi.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko yatumye Blue Trace protocol, ikoreshwa na porogaramu ya leta yemewe, ifunguye.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bibiri bigenzura sisitemu y'imikorere ya Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abakoraho; bavuga ko bazakomeza ubuzima bwite binyuze mu guhuza ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth rifite ingufu nke na encryption irinda ubuzima bwite.
Nanone kandi, basohoye ibisobanuro by'ikoranabuhanga ry'ingenzi rikoreshwa muri iyo gahunda.
Nk'uko Apple na Google babivuga, intego ni ugushyiraho gahunda mu byiciro bitatu, aribyo:
Gushyiraho ibikoresho bifasha leta gushyiraho porogaramu za leta zirinda ubuzima bwite kugira ngo zikurikirane Coronavirus
Kwishyira hamwe by'umwihariko muri Android na iOS nkuko Google na Apple bateganya gukemura ibibazo by'imikoreshereze n'ubugenzuzi bukomeje binyuze mu gutanga sisitemu mbere binyuze mu kuvugurura sisitemu y'imikorere hanyuma no kuyikura muri ubwo buryo nk'uko ubwo bugeragezo burangiye.
Gucuruza imiti (zwi no ku izina rya "re-use", "re-allocation", "change of purpose" cyangwa "therapeutic transformation") ni ugusubiza mu buryo imiti yemewe gukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara cyangwa uburwayi butandukanye n'ubwo yateguwe mu mizo ya mbere.
Ubwo ni bumwe mu buryo bwo gukora ubushakashatsi abashakashatsi barimo gukora kugira ngo bahingure imiti idahungabanya indwara ya COVID-19.
Mu bindi bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi harimo gukora urukingo rwa COVID-19 no gutwara plasma. Virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine zigera kuri 66 zishobora gukoreshwa imiti, buri poroteyine ikaba ifite ahantu henshi hahuza.
Gusuzuma aho izo nkingi zihurira bitanga igishushanyo mbonera cy'uburyo bwo gukora umuti wa virusi ukoresha neza wica poroteyine za COVID-19.
Mu maporoteyine SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane harimo protease ya ba-ba-bine, polymérase ya RNA ya RNA, heliase, protein S, na adenosine diphosphatase.
Hussain A.A., n'abandi, bize imiti myinshi y'abakandida nyuma yo kunozwa no gusesengurwa ku buryo ihuriyeho n'imiti yemewe ifite aho ihuriye cyane kugira ngo yihutishe iterambere ry'umuti ukomeye wa SARS-CoV-2 mu bushakashatsi bwe bwa mbere yo kuwugira inama mu buryo bw'ubushakashatsi.
Klorokin ni umuti wa malariya ukoreshwa n'abaganga mu kuvura indwara zimwe na zimwe z'umubiri.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine ifitanye isano na yo ishobora kuba mu miti ine iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi mu igerageza ry'ubufatanye mu buvuzi.
Guverineri wa New York, Andrew Cuomo, yatangaje ko igeragezwa rya leta ya New York kuri chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine rishobora gutangira ku ya 24 Werurwe. Ku ya 28 Werurwe, Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyemeje gukoresha hydroxychloroquine sulphate na chloroquine phosphate hakurikijwe uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (EUA).
Ubu buryo bwo kuvura ntabwo bwemejwe n'igerageza ry'ubuvuzi muri FDA kandi bwemewe n'uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu bihe by'impanuka gusa nk'uburyo bwo kugerageza bwo kuvura byihutirwa ku barwayi bari mu bitaro ariko badashobora kuvurwa mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi.
CDC yatangaje ko itaramenya "imikoreshereze ya hydroxychloroquine mu kwirinda cyangwa kuvura SARS-CoV-2, urugero cyangwa igihe".
Abaganga bavuze ko bakoresha ibiyobyabwenge iyo "nta kundi byagenda".
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Turukiya muri Istanbul ubu barimo bakora ubushakashatsi buto ku gukoresha chlorquine hamwe na zinc, vitamine A, vitamine C na vitamine D.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye bukorwa muri kaminuza ya Duke na Oxford.
Ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya Langone muri Kaminuza ya New York ririmo gukora igerageza ku mutekano n'ubushobozi bwa hydroxychloroquine mu kwirinda.
Ibizamini byo mu Bushinwa byabereye i Wuhan no mu mujyi wa Shenzhen byavuze ko imiti ya FAVIFIvir "ikora neza cyane".
Mu barwayi 35 bo mu mujyi wa Shenzhen, ibipimo byagize ingaruka mbi mu minsi 4, mu gihe abarwayi 45 batarabihawe bari bamaze iminsi 11 barwaye.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe i Wuhan ku barwayi 240 barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero, kimwe cya kabiri bahawe umuti witwa favipiravir, ikindi kimwe cya kabiri bahabwa umuti witwa omyfinovir.
Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani gishinzwe imiti cyakanguriye abantu ko ibimenyetso biriho bishyigikira iki kiyobyabwenge bidahagije kandi ko ari ibisanzwe.
Ku ya 2 Mata, Ubudage bwatangaje ko buzigura mu Buyapani kugira ngo buziyongere mu bubiko bwabwo, kandi ko ingabo zizazikoresha mu kugeza uyu muti ku bitaro bya kaminuza, aho uzakoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikinyamakuru South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe yagiranye ibiganiro by'ibanze n'ubuyobozi bwa Trump ku bijyanye no kugura uyu muti. Uyu muti ushobora kuba nta cyo umaze mu kuvura indwara zikomeye cyane aho virusi imaze kwiyongera.
Bishobora kuba bidakwiriye gukoreshwa n'abagore batwite cyangwa bashaka gutwita.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwakoresheje Lupinavir/Ritonavir (Calitra), umuti wa lupinavir na ritonavir, bwagaragaje ko nta nyungu zabyo zagaragaye.
Imiti yagenewe kubuza virusi itera SIDA kongera kwiyongera binyuze mu kuyikomatanya na protease.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Kaminuza ya Colorado barimo kugerageza guhindura imiti kugira ngo bagere ku cyuma gihuza SARS-CoV-2. Umuryango w'abahanga urimo kwibasirwa no kuyobora umutungo mu guhindura intego z'imiti yagenewe kuvura SIDA.
OMS yongeyeho Lupinavir/Ritonavir mu igerageza mpuzamahanga ry'ubwiyunge.
Gilead Sciences yatangije umuti wa Remdesivir mu kuvura indwara ya Ebola na Marburg virus. Gilead Sciences yaje kubona ko Remdesivir ifite ibikorwa bya virusi mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi ku virusi nyinshi za filigrane, za muco na coronaviruses.
Kimwe mu bibazo by'ubuvuzi bwa virusi ni uko ishobora kwihanganira indwara binyuze mu guhinduka kw'imiterere yayo, bishobora gutuma indwara zikomeye cyane zikwirakwira.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwo mu gihe cya mbere bwemeza ko Remdesivir ishobora kugira inzitizi y'ingirabuzima fatizo yo kurwanya indwara. Hariho ibigeragezo byinshi byo kwa muganga biriho, harimo bibiri bikorerwa ku bitaro bya Kaminuza ya Cleveland; kimwe ku barwayi bafite indwara yoroheje, ikindi ku barwayi bafite indwara ikomeye.
Hari ibizamini bitatu byagenewe imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi ya vitamini C ku barwayi bari mu bitaro barwaye cyane kubera COVID-19, hamwe n'ibizamini bibiri bigenzurwa hakoreshejwe imiti y'uburozi (Ubushinwa, Kanada) n'ikizamini kimwe kitagenzurwa (Ubutaliyani).
Leta ya New York yatangiye kugerageza imiti yitwa azithromycin ku itariki ya 24 Werurwe 2020.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'Ubuzima n'Ubuvuzi cy'u Buyapani (NCGM) kirateganya gukora igerageza mu buvuzi rikoresha Alvesco (cyclosonide) ikorwa na Teijin, corticosteroid ihumanywa mu kuvura asthma, mu kuvura abarwayi ba coronavirus nshya mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara.
Ubu hari igeragezwa ry'icyiciro cya kabiri rikoresha ubwoko bw'indwara ya angiotensin-2 ku barwayi 200 basabwa kwinjira mu igeragezwa ry'abarwayi bakomeye bari mu bitaro muri Danemark, Ubudage na Autriche kugira ngo hamenyekane niba umuti ufasha.
Abashakashatsi bo mu kigo cy'umutima cya Montreal muri Canada barimo kwiga uruhare rwa Colchicine mu kugabanya ubuhumekero n'ibibazo by'ubuhumekero mu barwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje bya COVID-19.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwiswe Kolkorona, bwakozwe ku bantu bakuru 6000 bafite imyaka 40 kuzamura, abaganga basanze bafite COVID-19 kandi bagaragaza ibimenyetso byoroheje batiriwe bajya mu bitaro.
Abagore batwite, bonsa cyangwa badafite uburyo bwiza bwo kuboneza urubyaro ntibashobora guhabwa ubu burenganzira.
Hari imiti myinshi igabanya amaraso igeragezwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubu heparin ifite ibiro bito by'imashini ikoreshwa cyane mu kuvura abarwayi, ibyo bikaba bisaba ko ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani gishinzwe imiti cyandika amabwiriza ku mikoreshereze yayo.
Ku itariki ya 14 Mata, hatangajwe ko mu Butaliyani hari ikigo kizakora ubushakashatsi ku barwayi 300, bugamije kureba niba inoxazapine sodium ishobora gukoreshwa mu rwego rwo kwirinda indwara no mu rwego rwo kuvura.
Kubera ko SARS-CoV-2 ari virusi, ubushakashatsi bw'ingenzi bwibanze ku kongera gukoresha imiti yemewe ya virusi yagenewe guhangana n'ibyorezo byabanje nk'indwara ya Mars, SARS, na virusi ya West Nile.
Ribavirin: Abahanga bagaragaje ko ribavirin ikoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19 hakurikijwe amabwiriza y'Ubushinwa yo ku nshuro ya karindwi.
Ominofer: Abahanga bagaragaje ko imiti ya Ominofer ikoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19 hakurikijwe amabwiriza ya 7 y'Ubushinwa.
Bimwe mu miti yica indwara z'ibyorezo by'indwara ya COVID-19 abahanga bagaragaje ko ishobora kongera gukoreshwa mu buvuzi harimo:
Toxilizumab (interloquin-6 receptor): yemejwe n'u Bushinwa.
Ibigeragezo byakozwe mu Butaliyani no mu Bushinwa. Reba Tosilizumab #COVID-19.
Urukingo rwa COVID-19 ni urukingo rwemewe ku ndwara ya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Nubwo nta rukingo rwigeze rusozwa mu igerageza, hari ingamba nyinshi zo gukora urwo rukingo.
Mu mpera za Gashyantare 2020, OMS yavuze ko itatekerezaga ko urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi iyitera, ruzabaho mu gihe kitarenze amezi 18.
Hari inkingo eshanu zari zitezweho mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi bw'ubuziranenge muri Mata.
COVID-19 yamenyekanye mu Ukuboza 2019.
Icyorezo gikomeye cyakwiriye isi yose mu 2020, bituma hashyirwaho amafaranga menshi kandi hakorwa ubushakashatsi mu gukora urukingo.
Imiryango myinshi ikoresha genomes zashyizwe ahagaragara mu gukora inkingo zishobora kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Icyemezo cya Coalition ku guhangana n'ibyorezo mu guhangana n'ibyorezo cyo gukora inkingo, cyatangajwe muri Mata, gisaba umuvuduko, ubushobozi bwo gukora, gukwirakwiza no kugera ku isi hose.
Muri Mata, abahanga mu bijyanye n'ubushakashatsi mu guhangana n'icyorezo batangaje ko mu ntangiriro za 2020, hari porogaramu 10 zitandukanye z'ikoranabuhanga zari mu bushakashatsi no mu iterambere mu gukora urukingo rukora neza rwa COVID-19.
Intego nyamukuru z'urubuga rugeze mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi ku budahemuka zirimo:
ADN (DNA ya RNA idafite ogisijeni na RNA ya RNA) (Umushinga wa mbere n'urukingo rw'umukandida: Moderna, na mRNA-1273)
Umurwayi wa virusi (umushinga w'icyiciro cya mbere n'urukingo rw'inkingo: Moderna, n'umurwayi wa virusi y'inkondo y'umura w'ubwoko bwa 5)
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'abahanga mu bijyanye n'ubushakashatsi mu guhangana n'ibyorezo muri Mata, hari inkingo 115 z'abakandida mu byiciro bya mbere by'iterambere, hamwe n'izindi 78 zemeza ko zikora (79, nk'uko ikigo Milken kibitangaza), n'izindi 37 zatangajwe, ariko amakuru y'ibanze make (ni ukuvuga ko ari mu igenamigambi cyangwa ari mu bikorwa) araboneka.
Icyiciro cya mbere n'icya kabiri ni igerageza ry'ibanze ku mutekano n'irinde, akenshi rifatwa ku buryo budasanzwe, rigenzurwa n'umwana, ahantu henshi, hagashyirwaho ibipimo by'ubwirinzi kandi bikora neza.
Ibizamini byo mu cyiciro cya gatatu bikunze kuba birimo umubare munini w'abitabiriye, harimo n'itsinda ry'ibanze, no gupima ubushobozi bw'urukingo mu gukumira indwara, hagenzurwa ingaruka mbi z'umuti mwiza.
Mu nkingo 79 z'abakandida ziri mu iterambere rikomeye (zemejwe mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020), 74 ntizirimo gusuzumwa ku bantu (zikirimo gushakishwa "imbere y'ivuriro").
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020 muri Ositaraliya, Kaminuza ya Queensland yatangaje ko irimo gukora iperereza ku buryo urukingo rwa 'clamp' rushobora guhindura poroteyine za virusi kugira ngo rutume umuntu agira ibisubizo by'ubudahangarwa.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020 muri Canada, Ikigo Mpuzamahanga cy'Incanco (VIDO-InterVac) cyo muri Kaminuza ya Saskatchewan cyatangaje ko cyatangiye gukora ku rukingo, kigamije gutangira igerageza ku bantu mu 2021.
Imishinga yo gukora inkingo yatangajwe mu kigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara ku ya 26 Mutarama 2020, no muri Kaminuza ya Hong Kong ku ya 28 Mutarama.
Ahagana ku ya 29 Mutarama 2020, ibigo by'ubuvuzi bya Janssen, byayobowe na Haneke Schweitzer, byatangaje ko byatangiye gukora urukingo.
Janssen ifatanyije na mugenzi wayo mu ikoranabuhanga mu by'ibinyabuzima, Vaxart, mu gukora urukingo rwo mu kanwa.
