Ku bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubu bushakashatsi bwibanze kuri poroteyine ya SpikeS ifasha virusi kwinjira mu byuma byakira ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni inkingo za ADN (inkingo za ADN z'umwimerere cyangwa za RNA ribose, ni uburyo bushya bwo gukora inkingo).
Inkingo z'igerageza ziterwa na bumwe muri ubwo buryo zigomba kugeragezwa kugira ngo zimenyekane ko zifite umutekano kandi ko zikora neza. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, igeragezwa rya mbere ry'urukingo ryatangiriye ku bantu bane bitangiye gukora muri Seattle.
Uru rukingo rufite kode y'ingirabuzima fatizo itagira icyo itwaye, yakuwe muri virusi itera iyo ndwara. Impamvu y'uko rukomeza kubaho bitewe n'umubiri w'ubundi bwoko bw'umubiri ni ikibazo gishobora kuvuka mu gukora urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, ariko ni impaka.
Hari ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 biri gukorwa guhera muri Mata 2020.
Hari ibizamini birindwi byakozwe ku miti yemewe ya malariya, harimo ine y'imiti yitwa hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Ibiyobyabwenge bya virusi bivugwamo kongera gukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara nshya ni byo byiganje mu bushakashatsi bw'Abashinwa, binyuze mu igerageza ry'icyiciro cya gatatu cya Remdesivir mu bihugu byinshi kandi ibisubizo byaryo biteganyijwe gutangazwa mu mpera za Mata.
Isesengura ry'imikorere y'inkingo n'imiti ishobora gukoreshwa muri COVID-19 ryakozwe guhera muri Mata 2020. Imiti myinshi ikoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19 irimo gusuzumwa, harimo Remdesivir, Chloroquine, Hydroxychloroquine, Lupinavir/Ritonavir na Lupinavir/Itonovair ivanze na Interferon beta.
Hari ibimenyetso by'ibanze byerekana ko Remdesivir igira ingaruka nziza, guhera muri Werurwe 2020.
Iterambere ry'ubuvuzi ryagaragaye mu barwayi bavuwe umuti wa Remdesivir wo gukoresha mu nda.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga byo mu cyiciro cya gatatu birakorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Chloroquine, yakoreshejwe mbere mu kuvura malariya, yagejejwe mu Bushinwa mu kwezi kwa kabiri 2020, kandi ifite ibisubizo by'ibanze.
Nyamara, hari amabwiriza yo gusuzuma ubushakashatsi.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bw'igihugu cya Koreya n'Ubushinwa bwemeza ko chlorokine ikoreshwa.
Icyakora, Ikigo cya Wuhan cyo Gushakisha Virusi kivuga ko nubwo abantu baterwa inkunga yo gufata igabano ry'igarama imwe, kurenza urugero rw'icyo gipimo bishobora guteza akaga kandi bishobora no gutuma umuntu apfa.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihuse hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine mu bushishozi bw'abaganga bavura abantu bafite COVID-19. Icyiciro cya 7 cy'amabwiriza y'Ubushinwa kandi kirimo interferon, ribevirin cyangwa omyfenovir yo gukoresha mu kuvura COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko ibipimo byinshi bya ribavirin ari ngombwa mu gupima SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi.
Ibindi byigwa byakozwe ku ngaruka za nitasoxanide ku binyabuzima byasabwe nyuma yo kugaragaza ko ihagarika ibipimo bike bya SARS-CoV-2. Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko gutangiza poroteyine ya spike na transmembrane serine protease 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa kugirango SARS-CoV-2 yinjire binyuze mu guhura na ACE2 receptor.
Ubushakashatsi bwa Chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa idafite, bwerekana ko hari ibyangiritse cyane byatumye umuryango w'abaganga utemera izo miti hatabayeho ubundi bushakashatsi. Oceltavir ntabwo ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi kandi nta ruhare ruzwi igira mu kuvura COVID-19.
Icyorezo cya sitokine gishobora kuba kimwe mu bibazo by'indwara ya COVID-19 mu gihe cy'amajyambere.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya inkubi y'umuyaga wa cytokine. Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'Ubushinwa yongereye Tusilizumab ku mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi nyuma yo kurangiza icyigisho gito.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'Ubutaliyani cyakoze igerageza ry'icyiciro cya 2 cy'ubushakashatsi ku bantu bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Uretse kuba ikoreshwa mu gupima Viratin mu maraso kugira ngo imenye ibiza bya cytokine, igamije kurwanya ibyo byorezo, bikekwa ko ari byo bituma abantu bamwe na bamwe bicwa.
Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyemeje uburyo bwo kuvura interleukin-6 receptor, ubuvuzi bw'utugingo twa T-cell twa Khemiri, hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gusubiza inyuma ku buvuzi bwa sitokine ituma umuntu adashobora gukoresha steroid mu mwaka wa 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya ihamye y'uko Tocilizumab ari umuti mwiza wa sitokine.
Uburyo bwo gutwara abasirikare b'umubiri basukuye kandi bifatanyije butangwa n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bw'abantu bakize COVID-19 ku bakenera ubu bugomba kwigwa nk'uburyo butari ubwisungane mu gukingira.
Ubwo buryo bwakozwe ku barwayi ba SARS, ariko nta cyo bwagezeho.
Kugabanya virusi ni uburyo bwo gukora bwitezwe, aho imiti y'abanduye ishobora gukoreshwa nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko, hari ubundi buryo bushobora gukoreshwa, nk'uburozi bw'ingirabuzimafatizo cyangwa uburozi bw'amaraso cyangwa byombi.
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kuvura abarwayi ku buryo budafite ingaruka, nko gukoresha abarwayi ku buryo bw'imikorere, buri gukorwa.
Umusaruro wa serumu ya serumu y'umutsi, igizwe n'igice cy'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize kandi gifite udukoko tw'ubwirinzi bwihariye kuri iyi virusi, ushobora kwiyongera kugira ngo ikwirakwizwe vuba.
Indwara ziterwa na koronavirusi, ni indwara zitandukanye cyane.
Li Wen Liang, umuganga wo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan, nyuma yaje kurwara ndetse arapfa azize COVID-19 nyuma yo gukangurira abantu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
